%20school%20run%20by%20the%20Pune-based%20Maharashtra%20Institute%20of%20Technology-World%20Peace%20University%20(MIT-WPU)%2C%20got%20a%20rude%20shock%20as%20her%20award%20was%20cancelled%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20award%20presentation%20ceremony%2C%20which%20was%20held%20in%20the%20institute%E2%80%99s%20premises%20today.%20The%20award%20was%20cancelled%20by%20the%20university%E2%80%99s%20management%20in%20the%20face%20of%20right-wing%20political%20pressure%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20learned.%20The%20institute%20authorities%20were%20tightlipped%20about%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENabi%E2%80%99s%20report%2C%20%E2%80%98The%20half%20widows%20of%20Kashmir%E2%80%99%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1015849%2Fhow-kashmirs-half-widows-are-denied-their-basic-property-rights%5C%22%3Eappearing%20in%20%3Cem%3EScroll%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20had%20been%20chosen%20the%20winner%20in%20the%20category%20of%20%E2%80%98journalism%20that%20promoted%20empathy%2C%20understanding%20and%20inclusivity%20in%20society%E2%80%99.%20It%20brought%20out%20the%20longstanding%20plight%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98half%20widows%E2%80%99%20of%20Kashmir%20who%20continue%20to%20be%20denied%20their%20property%20rights%20decades%20after%20the%20disappearance%20of%20their%20husbands.%20The%20reporting%20for%20the%20story%20was%20aided%20by%20the%20Pulitzer%20Centre%20on%20Crisis%20Reporting.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHer%20story%20had%20been%20unanimously%20chosen%20from%20dozens%20of%20entries%20by%20a%20seven-member%20jury%20comprising%20three%20members%20from%20the%20institute%20and%20four%20external%20members%2C%20namely%20Sunanda%20Mehta%2C%20resident%20editor%20of%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Pune%20edition%2C%20Sandeep%20Adhwaryu%2C%20cartoonist%20at%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20of%3C%2Fem%3E%20India%2C%20Sajeev%20Ratna%20Singh%2C%20head%20of%20the%20journalism%20school%20at%20Bennett%20University%20and%20M.K.%20Venu%2C%20founding%20editor%20of%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENabi%20had%20been%20informed%20that%20she%20had%20won%20the%20award%20in%20a%20phone%20call%20from%20the%20director%2C%20Department%20of%20Media%20%26amp%3B%20Communication%20at%20MIT-WPU%20Dhiraj%20Singh%2C%20as%20well%20as%20an%20email%20from%20him%2C%20on%20October%2011.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20288px)%2085vw%2C%20288px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18132418%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-18-at-1.18.14-PM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22288%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18132418%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-18-at-1.18.14-PM.jpeg%20553w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18132418%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-18-at-1.18.14-PM-138x300.jpeg%20138w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18132418%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-18-at-1.18.14-PM-472x1024.jpeg%20472w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-680617%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22625%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20email%20Safina%20Nabi%20received.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ENabi%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20institute%20had%20made%20arrangements%20for%20her%20to%20travel%20for%20the%20award%20ceremony%2C%20and%20she%20was%20supposed%20to%20leave%20on%20October%2017%20for%20Pune.%20However%2C%20on%20the%20afternoon%20of%20October%2016%2C%20she%20received%20a%20call%20from%20an%20unknown%20faculty%20member%20who%20said%20the%20award%20had%20been%20cancelled%20and%20so%20she%20should%20no%20longer%20travel%20to%20Pune.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEverything%20was%20in%20place%20and%20for%20a%20week%20they%20kept%20reaching%20out%20for%20travel%20arrangements%20etc%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20supposed%20to%20travel%20on%20the%2017th%20of%20October%20and%20on%20the%2016th%20of%20October%20around%202%20o%E2%80%99clock%20in%20the%20afternoon%20I%20received%20a%20call%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20phone%20was%20a%20woman%20who%20introduced%20herself%20as%20one%20of%20the%20faculty%20members%20of%20the%20university.%20She%20mentioned%20that%20they%20are%20canceling%20my%20award%20and%20I%20am%20not%20supposed%20to%20travel%20now.%20When%20I%20asked%20for%20the%20reasons%20she%20mentioned%20that%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20political%20pressure%20that%20they%20are%20facing%20for%20awarding%20me.%20She%20also%20said%20it%20would%20be%20highly%20risky%20for%20me%20to%20travel%20or%20be%20present%20at%20the%20venue.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThinking%20that%20this%20was%20some%20sort%20of%20a%20prank%20call%2C%20Nabi%20then%20reached%20out%20to%20Rajeesh%20Kumar%20who%20is%20an%20assistant%20professor%20at%20the%20Department%20of%20Mass%20Communication%20and%20Journalism%20to%20check%20about%20the%20authenticity%2C%20as%20he%20had%20been%20her%20single%20point%20of%20contact%20till%20then.%20%E2%80%9CTo%20my%20surprise%2C%20he%20was%20clueless%20and%20requested%20to%20be%20given%20some%20time%20to%20cross-check%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20called%20me%20back%20sometime%20and%20confirmed%20that%20they%20were%20actually%20canceling%20my%20award%20and%20he%20was%20sorry.%20I%20requested%20they%20put%20all%20of%20this%20over%20email%20and%20give%20me%20the%20reasons%20as%20to%20why%20are%20they%20doing%20so.%20After%20this%20Dhiraj%20Singh%20called%20me%20who%20mentioned%20the%20same%20thing%20and%20didn%E2%80%99t%20agree%20to%20put%20anything%20over%20email.%20They%20were%20just%20calling%20me%20and%20giving%20me%20the%20reason%20that%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20political%20pressure%20on%20the%20university%20not%20to%20felicitate%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ENabi%20then%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20jury%2C%20who%20too%20had%20not%20been%20told%20abo