20and%20thematic%20leitmotif%20of%20%3Cem%3EKaala%20Paani%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20hardly%20surprising%20for%20a%20tale%20that%20unfolds%20in%20a%20part%20of%20India%20that%20is%20walled%20in%20by%20the%20ocean%20on%20all%20sides.%20Its%20contamination%20mirrors%20the%20toxicity%20that%20has%20seeped%20into%20the%20air%20and%20the%20land%20that%20make%20up%20the%20islands.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20moral%20conundrums%20that%20the%20medical%20fraternity%20and%20the%20Lieutenant-Governor's%20office%20face%20pertain%20to%20the%20pressing%20need%20to%20save%20the%20infected%20population%2C%20prevent%20the%20disease%20from%20spreading%2C%20control%20the%20movement%20of%20people%2C%20and%20adopt%20measures%20to%20minimize%20the%20impact%20of%20panic%20reactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F6ph4WPZIrbM%3Fsi%3Dt9z68RrC-sMQ_CEC%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESet%20in%20the%20near%20future%20but%20spanning%20multiple%20decades%20with%20flashbacks%20setting%20the%20context%20and%20snatches%20of%20dialogue%20alluding%20to%20hoary%20times%2C%20%3Cem%3EKaala%20Paani%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20written%20by%20Biswapati%20Sarkar%20and%20directed%20by%20Saxena%20and%20Amit%20Golani%2C%20abounds%20in%20thrills%2C%20tragic%20turns%20of%20events%20and%20individuals%20weighed%20down%20by%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20year%20is%202027.%20The%20Covid-19%20pandemic%20is%20still%20fresh%20in%20the%20minds%20of%20people.%20The%20Kaala%20Paani%20storyline%20looks%20beyond%20disease%20and%20devastation%20and%20blends%20fiction%20and%20truth%20to%20delve%20into%20the%20reasons%20behind%20the%20public%20health%20crisis%20-%20deforestation%2C%20threats%20posed%20to%20an%20endangered%20indigenous%20community%2C%20industry-government%20nexus%20and%20corruption%20at%20various%20levels%20of%20the%20local%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20sense%20of%20dread%20and%20gloom%20pervades%20the%20islands%20as%20Leptospiral%20Hemorrhagic%20Fever%20(LHF-27)%20turns%20rampant.%20Citizens%20and%20medical%20professionals%20are%20up%20against%20an%20enemy%20that%20is%20invisible%2C%20Nature%2C%20which%20has%20borne%20the%20brunt%20of%20mankind's%20greed%20for%20centuries%20and%20is%20now%20striking%20back.%20The%20seven-episode%20series%20derives%20strength%20from%20the%20ethical%2C%20psychological%20and%20environmental%20questions%20that%20it%20raises.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20Panchatantra%20story%20about%20a%20frog%20and%20a%20scorpion%20is%20used%20to%20underline%20the%20nature%20of%20goodness%20and%20dishonesty%20in%20present%20times.%20The%20%26quot%3Btrolley%20problem%26quot%3B%20thought%20experiment%20alludes%20to%20the%20situation%20on%20the%20ground%20-%20the%20administration%20is%20in%20a%20make-or-break%20moral%20quandary.%20Is%20it%20fine%20to%20sacrifice%20one%20person%20in%20order%20to%20save%20thousands%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EKaala%20Paani%3C%2Fem%3E%20situates%20numerous%20significant%20stories%2C%20contemporary%20and%20historical%2C%20in%20the%20collective%20and%20the%20personal%20in%20search%20of%20an%20answer%20to%20that%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%C2%A0%3Cem%3EKaala%20Paani%3C%2Fem%3E%20cast%20is%20led%20by%20Mona%20Singh%20and%20Ashutosh%20Gowariker%20but%20it%20is%20Sukant%20Goel%2C%20playing%20a%20Port%20Blair%20taxi%20operator%2C%20who%20hogs%20the%20lion's%20share%20of%20the%20spotlight.%20The%20gifted%20actor%20does%20full%20justice%20to%20a%20strong%20author-backed%20role%20that%20allows%20him%20to%20mine%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20emotions%2C%20from%20the%20frothy%20and%20flippant%20to%20the%20intense%20and%20unsettling.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlso%20impressive%20are%20the%20key%20supporting%20actors%2C%20each%20playing%20a%20character%20with%20a%20past%20marred%20by%20trauma%20and%20unpleasant%20experiences%20that%20take%20some%20doing%20to%20live%20down.%20From%20violence%20to%20toxic%20masculinity%20and%20social%20ostracism%20to%20professional%20hurdles%2C%20these%20individuals%20have%20been%20though%20a%20lot%20and%20what%20they%20encounter%20during%20the%20epidemic%20is%20an%20opportunity%20for%20them%20to%20redeem%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVikas%20Kumar%20plays%20Santosh%20Savla%2C%20a%20tourist%20from%20Bokaro%20who%20has%20travelled%20to%20Andaman%20and%20Nicobar%20Islands%20with%20his%20wife%20and%20two%20children%20to%20attend%20a%20tourist%20festival.%20The%20man%2C%20benign%20and%20soft-hearted%2C%20banks%20upon%20his%20wife%20Gargi%20(Sarika%20Singh)%20to%20be%20the%20family's%20pillar%20of%20strength%20through%20thick%20and%20thin.%20In%20a%20severe%20crisis%20situation%2C%20Santosh%20has%20to%20dig%20deep%20into%20his%20reserves%20of%20endurance%20as%20he%20is%20buffeted%20by%20separation%2C%20loss%20and%20bereavement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EArushi%20Sharma%20is%20Jyotsna%20Dey%2C%20an%20aspiring%20nurse%20who%20has%20abandoned%20her%20ambition%20following%20a%20violent%20incident%20in%20Pune%20that%20has%20singed%20her%20for%20good.%20Her%20shot%20at%20redemption%20rests%20on%20ensuring%20the%20safety%20of%20two%20children%20separated%20from%20their%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERadhika%20Mehrotra%20plays%20medical%20intern%20Ritu%20Gagra%2C%20who%20joins%20the%20team%20of%20Dr%20Soudamini%20Singh%20(Mona%20Singh)%2C%20a%20grouchy%2C%20cynical%20but%20exceptionally%20committed%20professional%20who%20lives%20with%20a%20German%20Shepherd%20aptly%20called%20Mister%2C%20as%20the%20latter's%20hospital%20faces%20a%20severe%20staff%20shortage%20in%20the%20face%20of%20the%20health%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmey%20Wagh%20delivers%20an%20energetic%20but%20delightfully%20layered%20performance%20as%20police%20officer%20Ketan%20Kamat%2C%20a%20man%20given%20to%20fishing%20in%20troubled%20waters%20and%20saving%20his%20own%20skin%20come%20what%20may.%20And%20Chinmay%20Mandlekar%20gets%20into%20the%20skin%20of%20a%20doctor%20under%20understandable%20duress%20aggravated%20by%20a%20tragedy%20that%20hits%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20major%20tourist%20festival%20is%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20away%20and%20thousands%20of%20visitors%20have%20arrived%20in%20Port%20Blair.%20Panic%20spreads%20as%20word%20gets%20around%20that%20a%20mysterious%20killer%20disease%20has%20descended%20on%20the%20islands.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20administration%2C%20led%20by%20Admiral%20Zibran%20Qadri%20(Asuthosh%20Gowariker)%2C%20the%20central%20hospital%20under%20Dr%20Soudamini%20Singh's%20charge%2C%20individuals%20like%20Chiranjeevi%20(Sukant%20Goel)%20whose%20livelihood%20depends%20on%20the%20influx%20of%20tourists%20and%20infected%20locals%20and%20several%20outsiders%20are%20sucked%20into%20the%20maelstrom.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20crisis%20is%2C%20of%20course%2C%20not%20directly%20of%20the%20tourists'%20making.%20The%20plunder%20of%20tribal%20land%20and%20unsustainable%20development%20models%20have%20pushed%20the%20scenic%20islands%20to%20the%20brink.%20A%20multi-billion-dollar%20MNC%2C%20with%20the%20connivance%20of%20elements%20in%20the%20bureaucracy%20and%20the%20police%2C%20seeks%20to%20extend%20its%20hold%20on%20the%20land%20the%20forests%20stand%20on%20and%20the%20people%20that%20the%20forests%20belong%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20struggle%20to%20save%20lives%20coincides%20with%20the%20race%20to%20find%20the%20cause%20of%20the%20epidemic%20and%20a%20cure.%20The%20narrative%20revolves%20around%20the%20fate%20on%20endangered%20indigenous%20community%20that%20has%20lives%20in%20the%20forest%20for%2060%2C000%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EKaala%20Paani%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20well-acted%2C%20wonderfully%20crafted%20and%20consistently%20watchable%20drama%20the%20skirts%20around%20the%20pitfalls%20of%20a%20multi-pronged%20narrative.%20It%20devises%20ways%20not%20to%20let%20one%20thematic%20idea%20get%20in%20the%20way%20of%20another.%20All%20the%20strands%20come%20together%20ne