ent%2C%20the%20three%20recruiters%20said%20they%20look%20for%20%26quot%3Bsoft%20skills%26quot%3B%20like%20strong%20communication%2C%20the%20ability%20to%20collaborate%2C%20and%20adaptability%20to%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2)%20Demonstrate%20your%20interest%20in%20AI%20during%20the%20interview%20%E2%80%94%20and%20be%20able%20to%20prove%20it%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20lucky%20enough%20to%20land%20an%20interview%2C%20be%20prepared%20to%20talk%20about%20your%20interest%20in%20generative%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlex%20Shapiro%2C%20the%20chief%20people%20officer%20at%20Jasper%20AI%2C%20an%20AI%20marketing%20and%20writing%20software%20that%20Shapiro%20said%20recently%20completed%20its%20%26quot%3Bkey%20hiring%26quot%3B%20over%20the%20last%20three%20years%2C%20said%20she%20expects%20job%20candidates%20to%20show%20that%20they've%20%26quot%3Bdone%20their%20homework%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bunderstand%20the%20technology.%26quot%3B%20For%20instance%2C%20she%20said%20that%20candidates%20for%20engineering%20roles%20should%20be%20able%20to%20differentiate%20between%20a%20%26quot%3Bmodel%20layer%26quot%3B%20and%20an%20%26quot%3Bapp%20layer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20technical%20and%20non-technical%20roles%20alike%2C%20interviewees%20can%20stand%20out%20if%20they%20can%20articulate%20how%20they've%20been%20playing%20around%20with%20generative%20AI%20tools%20like%20ChatGPT.%20This%20especially%20applies%20to%20those%20interviewing%20for%20client-facing%20roles%20like%20customer%20service%20as%20it%20shows%20%26quot%3Bwhether%20or%20not%20people%20have%20dived%20into%20this%20industry%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20a%20new%20field%2C%20I%20think%20what%20helps%20us%20to%20differentiate%20people%20is%20just%20how%20much%20curiosity%20they've%20had%20about%20the%20space%20and%20what%20work%20they've%20done%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Shapiro%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFoltz%2C%20the%20chief%20talent%20officer%20at%20IBM%2C%20would%20agree%20with%20Shapiro.%20He%20said%20that%20applicants%20who%20read%20AI%20research%20papers%2C%20follow%20AI%20forums%2C%20and%20explore%20AI-related%20online%20courses%20stand%20out%20from%20the%20pool%20because%20it%20shows%20they%20are%20genuinely%20curious%20about%20AI%20and%20have%20a%20%26quot%3Bdesire%20to%20continuously%20learn.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3)%20Don't%20expect%20your%20ChatGPT%20skills%20to%20get%20you%20hired%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20AI%20tools%20like%20ChatGPT%20can%20be%20useful%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fusing-ai-write-resume-chatgpt-job-search-cover-letter-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewriting%20your%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-write-cover-letter-chatgpt-template-prompts-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecover%20letters%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20make%20sure%20you%20double-check%20the%20AI-generated%20documents%20for%20accuracy%20before%20submitting%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShapiro%20acknowledged%20that%20using%20ChatGPT%20can%20be%20%26quot%3Bgreat%26quot%3B%20in%20helping%20applicants%20%26quot%3Bbrainstorm%20verbs%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bbring%20a%20level%20of%20polish%26quot%3B%20to%20their%20applications.%20However%2C%20she%20urges%20applicants%20to%20make%20sure%20their%20AI-generated%20documents%20accurately%20reflect%20their%20qualities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20there's%20been%20times%20when%20Jasper%20recruiters%20interviewed%20candidates%20and%20discovered%20that%20there's%20a%20skill%20in%20their%20resume%20they%20didn't%20intend%20to%20be%20there%2C%20or%20a%20characterization%20they're%20not%20familiar%20with%2C%20which%20she%20said%20could%20lead%20to%20problems%20down%20the%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20ChatGPT%20can%20actually%20hurt%20an%20applicant's%20chances%20of%20moving%20forward%20in%20the%20hiring%20process%20if%20the%20chatbot%20is%20used%20irresponsibly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuran%20from%20Nvidia%20said%20there's%20been%20instances%20where%20recruiters%20at%20her%20company%20caught%20candidates%20using%20ChatGPT%20during%20interviews%20to%20answer%20questions%2C%20which%20she%20said%20is%20prohibited.%20Coronini%20from%20Hugging%20Face%20has%20even%20seen%20cover%20letters%20that%20include%20prompts%20like%20%26quot%3BInsert%20a%20cover%20letter%20in%20order%20to%20explain%20why%20my%20background%20is%20a%20good%20fit%20for%20this%20role%26quot%3B%20used%20to%20generate%20them%20%E2%80%94%20which%20he%20calls%20a%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3Breally%20bad%26quot%3B%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20me%2C%20this%20is%20a%20showstopper%2C%20because%20it%20doesn't%20really%20show%20your%20motivation%20to%20join%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E4)%20Don't%20be%20afraid%20to%20apply%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20you%20don't%20meet%20all%20of%20the%20job%20requirements%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20AI%20job%20listings%20may%20require%20applicants%20to%20have%20college%20or%20higher%20level%20degrees%20in%20computer%20science%20and%20engineering.%20But%20all%20the%20recruiters%20who%20spoke%20to%20Insider%20said%20they%20wouldn't%20rule%20out%20applicants%20who%20have%20less%20conventional%20backgrounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFoltz%20said%20that%20IBM%20focuses%20on%20%26quot%3Bprioritizing%20skills%20and%20experiences%26quot%3B%20over%20%26quot%3Btraditional%20degrees%26quot%3B%20if%20they%20can%20demonstrate%20a%20%26quot%3Bfoundational%20understanding%20of%20AI%2C%20whether%20that's%20knowing%20how%20to%20apply%20AI%20to%20their%20workflows%2C%20or%20taking%20%26quot%3Bindustry-recognized%26quot%3B%20online%20courses%20on%20AI%20and%20machine%20learning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20education%20and%20AI%20experience%2C%20Duran%20said%20applicants%20from%20non-traditional%20backgrounds%20can%20shine%20if%20they%20can%20%26quot%3Bclearly%20communicate%20what%20makes%20them%20stand%20out%26quot%3B%20by%20emphasizing%20their%20career%20milestones%2C%20leadership%20capabilities%2C%20and%20the%20impact%20of%20their%20previous%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20cases%2C%20Shapiro%20said%20workers%20with%20less%20conventional%20backgrounds%20may%20have%20more%20to%20offer%20than%20those%20with%20technical%20degrees.%20She%20said%20that%20Jasper%20hired%20employees%20who%20completed%20skills-based%20boot%20camps%20and%20believes%20that%20applicants%20who%20are%20career%20changers%20can%20be%20more%20equipped%20for%20particular%20roles%20than%20those%20with%20technical%20degrees%20%E2%80%94%20if%20they%20take%20the%20initiative%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20everything%20that's%20happening%20in%20generative%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20really%20valuable%20to%20have%20people%20come%20in%20from%20different%20perspectives%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-ai-job-career-ibm-nvidia-recruiters-advice-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697616601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6528567755f52b01b35e6857%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-ai-job-career-ibm-nvidia-recruiters-advice-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Recruiters%20say%20applicants%20don't%20always%20need%20college%20degrees%2C%20but%20should%20be%20able%20to%20demonstrate%20AI%20interest.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22amok%40insider.com%20(Aaron%20Mok)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-ai-job-career-ibm-nvidia-recruiters-advice-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gaza%20Residents%20Thought%20Hospitals%20Were%20Safe%20Spaces.%20Last%20Night%20Changed%20That%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20Gaza's%20Al%20Ahli%20Arab%20hospital%20was%20bombed%20last%20night%2C%20many%20of%20those%20inside%20were%20neither%20ill%20nor%20injured.%20They%20had%20moved%20in%20after%20losing%20their%20homes%20in%20the%20war%20triggered%20by%20Hamas'%20shocking%20attacks%20on%20October%207.%20They%20had%20hoped%20the%20hospital%20would%20be%20a%20safe%20shelter%20amid%20Israel's%20brutal%20counterstrike.%20Last%20night%20proved%20them%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20strike%20on%20the%20hospital%20in%20central%20Gaza%20killed%20at%20least%20500%20people%2C%20news%20agency%20Reuters%20reported%2C%20quoting%20Gaza%20officials.%20While%20the%20local%20Hamas%20leadership%20has%20accused%20Israel%20of%20striking%20the%20hospital%2C%20Tel%20Aviv%20has%20claimed%20that%20a%20rocket%20misfired%20by%20Islamic%20Jihad%20Palestinian%20militants%20hit%20the%20health%20facility.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22About%20a%20million%20people%20have%20been%20displaced%20in%20Gaza%20since%20war%20began%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22About%20a%20million%20people%20have%20been%20displaced%20in%20Gaza%20since%20war%20began%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fpvfd260g_gaza-reuters_625x300_18_October_23.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EAbout%20a%20million%20people%20have%20been%20displaced%20in%20Gaza%20since%20war%20began%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cspan%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20Reuters%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHospitals%20As%20Shelters%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20a%20million%20people%20out%20of%20Gaza's%202%20million%20population%20are%20currently%20homeless%2C%20according%20to%20UN%20estimates.%20While%20a%20section%20of%20them%20have%20been%20accommodated%20in%20shelters%20run%20by%20humanitarian%20organisations%2C%20many%20others%20have%20taken%20shelter%20where%20they%20found%20it.%20Tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20families%20have%20moved%20into%20hospitals.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20health%20ministry%20in%20Hamas-ruled%20territory%20has%20said%20Ahli%20Arab%20hospital%20was%20sheltering%20not%20only%20hundreds%20of%20sick%20and%20wounded%2C%20but%20also%20people%20%26quot%3Bforcibly%20displaced%20from%20their%20homes%26quot%3B%20because%20of%20other%20strikes.%20According%20to%20an%20AFP%20report%2C%20corridors%20at%20Nasser%20Hospital%20in%20Gaza%20were%20full%20of%20women%20making%20bread%20and%20drying%20clothes%20as%20doctors%20fought%20to%20save%20lives%20inside.%20%26quot%3BDeath%20might%20be%20more%20merciful%2C%26quot%3B%20Amira%2C%2044%2C%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael%20forces%20had%20earlier%20asked%20Gaza%20residents%20to%20move%20south%20as%20they%20intensify%20their%20attack%20against%20Hamas.%20Tel%20Aviv%20has%20claimed%20Hamas%20is%20blocking%20people%20from%20escaping%20so%20that%20they%20can%20use%20them%20as%20human%20shields.%20Also%2C%20the%20Rafah%20border%20to%20Gaza's%20south%2C%20the%20escape%20route%20into%20Egypt%2C%20has%20been%20shut%20since%20the%20war%20began.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHospitals%20Under%20Attack%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20many%20as%20111%20healthcare%20facilities%20or%20vehicles%20have%20been%20targeted%20since%20the%20war%20began%20on%20October%207%2C%20the%20World%20Health%20Organization%20has%20said.%20Twelve%20health%20workers%20have%20died%20and%2024%20health%20facilities%2C%20six%20of%20them%20hospitals%2C%20damaged.%20According%20to%20the%20WHO%20report%2C%20three%20hospitals%20have%20suffered%20heavy%20damage%20to%20the%20point%20that%20they%20are%20no%20longer%20functioning.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Thousands%20have%20taken%20shelter%20in%20Gazas%20hospitals%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Thousands%20have%20taken%20shelter%20in%20Gazas%20hospitals%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Ffsue9vn_gaza-hospitals_625x300_18_October_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThousands%20have%20taken%20shelter%20in%20Gaza's%20hospitals%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cspan%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20PTI%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20hospitals%20that%20are%20still%20running%20have%20been%20hit%20by%20the%20blackout%20in%20Gaza%20after%20Israel%20cut%20off%20electricity%20to%20the%20Strip.%20Officials%20in%20Gaza%20have%20been%20directing%20to%20hospitals%20fuel%20available%20in%20other%20public%20facilities%20to%20prevent%20a%20complete%20shutdown%2C%20a%20UN%20report%20said.%20People%20are%20also%20being%20requested%20to%20donate%20fuel%20set%20aside%20for%20domestic%20consumption%20so%20that%20the%20hospitals%20can%20keep%20functioning.%20The%20situation%20has%20been%20worsened%20as%20supply%20of%20medicines%20runs%20out.%20%26quot%3BAn%20estimated%2050%2C000%20pregnant%20women%20face%20extreme%20challenges%20to%20accessing%20prenatal%20and%20maternity%20care%20due%20to%20risks%20related%20to%20movement%2C%20the%20halt%20of%20health%20facilities%2C%20and%20shortage%20of%20lifesaving%20supplies%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20UN%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECrowding%20Sparks%20Infection%20Fears%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20more%20people%20reach%20hospitals%20in%20the%20hope%20of%20escaping%20Israel's%20airstrikes%2C%20the%20health%20facilities%20face%20risks%20of%20disease%20outbreaks%20and%20a%20hygiene%20crisis.%20Speaking%20to%20AFP%2C%20Amira%20at%20Nasser%20Hospital%20said%20it%20has%20been%20a%20week%20since%20they%20could%20take%20a%20shower.%20%26quot%3BOur%20bodies%20itch%20all%20over.%20It%20has%20been%20a%20week%20since%20we%20could%20take%20a%20shower%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20is%20no%20better%20at%20Dar%20al-Shifa%20hospital%2C%20the%20biggest%20healthcare%20unit%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIbrahim%20Teyssir%2C%20one%20of%20thousands%20seeking%20refuge%20there%2C%20told%20AFP%2C%20%26quot%3BNo%20one%20has%20pity%20on%20us.%20What%20have%20we%20done%20to%20deserve%20this%3F%20What%20have%20our%20children%20done%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20WHO%20has%20said%20hospitals%20are%20at%20a%20%26quot%3Bbreaking%20point%20and%20are%20overflowing%20and%20with%20people%20desperately%20seeking%20a%20safe%20shelter%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F43nhp8jg_gaza-reuters_625x300_18_October_23.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20Gaza%20hospitals%20are%20overflowing%20with%20patients%20as%20supplies%20run%20out%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCrowding%20is%20getting%20worse.%20Over%2030%2C000%20people%20are%20sheltering%20at%20Shifa%20Hospital%20alone%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20UN%20agency%20told%20AFP%2C%20quoting%20Hamas%20health%20officials.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20extremely%20concerned%20about%20disease%20outbreaks%20due%20to%20mass%20displacement%20and%20poor%20water%20and%20sanitation%20among%20people%20who%20are%20already%20in%20a%20dire%20situation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BDeath%20Sentence%26quot%3B%20And%20An%20SOS%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20order%20to%20evacuate%20northern%20Gaza%20as%20it%20widens%20its%20offensive%20has%20drawn%20a%20sharp%20response%20from%20WHO.%20The%20WHO%20said%20moving%202%2C000%20patients%20to%20hospitals%20that%20are%20already%20overflowing%20with%20patients%20could%20be%20%26quot%3Btantamount%20to%20a%20death%20sentence%26quot%3B.%20The%20health%20body%20has%20called%20for%20an%20immediate%20end%20to%20hostilities%20and%20a%20humanitarian%20corridor%20to%20ensure%20health%20supplies%20reach%20hospitals.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20WHO%20has%20also%20raised%20an%20alarm%20on%20how%20lack%20of%20funding%20may%20cut%20access%20to%20essential%20health%20services.%20Gaza's%20health%20sector%20was%20reeling%20under%20a%20fund%20crunch%20even%20before%20the%20war%2C%20and%20the%20violence%20has%20made%20matters%20much%20worse.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Inter-Agency%20Flash%20Appeal%2C%20released%20on%2013%20October%20estimated%20that%20%24%2023.1%20million%20were%20needed%20for%20the%20immediate%20response%2C%20however%20this%20figure%20will%20only%20continue%20to%20rise%20as%20the%20situation%20unfolds%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20has%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20unless%20funding%20comes%20in%2C%20thousands%20will%20lose%20access%20to%20basic%20healthcare%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697616420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fp8v0ef38_gaza-hospital_625x300_18_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-gaza-war-israel-hamas-war-gaza-hospital-attack-gaza-residents-thought-hospitals-were-safe-spaces-last-night-changed-that-4491945%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20Gaza's%20Al%20Ahli%20Arab%20hospital%20was%20bombed%20last%20night%2C%20many%20of%20those%20inside%20were%20neither%20ill%20nor%20injured.%20They%20had%20moved%20in%20after%20losing%20their%20homes%20in%20the%20war%20triggered%20by%20Hamas'%20shocking%20attacks%20on%20October%207.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-gaza-war-israel-hamas-war-gaza-hospital-attack-gaza-residents-thought-hospitals-were-safe-spaces-last-night-changed-that-4491945%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-gaza-war-israel-hamas-war-gaza-hospital-attack-gaza-residents-thought-hospitals-were-safe-spaces-last-night-changed-that-4491945%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-gaza-war-israel-hamas-war-gaza-hospital-attack-gaza-residents-thought-hospitals-were-safe-spaces-last-night-changed-that-4491945%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20As%20Israel-Hamas%20Crisis%20Escalates%2C%20Indian%20Diplomacy%20Under%20Pressure%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20tensions%20continue%20to%20escalate%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20diplomacy%20too%20has%20picked%20up%20pace%20with%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20deciding%20to%20visit%20Israel%20to%20assess%20Israeli%20plans.%20After%20the%20attack%20on%20a%20Gaza%20hospital%20last%20night%20left%20500%20dead%20and%20amid%20reports%20of%20an%20impending%20Israeli%20ground%20offensive%2C%20there%20are%20growing%20concerns%20about%20the%20humanitarian%20toll%20and%20its%20long%20term%20costs.%C2%A0There%20is%20the%20issue%20of%20hostages%20and%20of%20providing%20aid%20to%20Gaza%20that%20must%20be%20shaping%20the%20calculus%20of%20Israel%20and%20its%20allies.%20Iran%2C%20for%20its%20part%2C%20has%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20Israel%20will%20not%20be%20allowed%20to%20act%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20without%20consequences%20and%20has%20warned%20of%20%26quot%3Bpre-emptive%20action.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20world%20is%20starkly%20divided%20on%20the%20issue%20with%20the%20emerging%20geopolitical%20faultlines%20further%20getting%20solidified.%20These%20divisions%20are%20also%20getting%20manifested%20within%20nations.%20In%20the%20West%2C%20countries%20are%20struggling%20to%20contain%20domestic%20schisms%2C%20with%20some%20even%20facing%20terror%20incidents%20as%20passions%20get%20inflamed%20and%20troublemakers%20try%20to%20make%20the%20most%20of%20it.%20In%20this%20battle%2C%20universities%20in%20the%20West%20have%20emerged%20as%20the%20new%20battlegrounds%20as%20competing%20narratives%20contend%20with%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGiven%20India's%20growing%20stakes%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20it%20too%20can't%20remain%20immune%20to%20the%20reverberations%20from%20its%20extended%20neighbourhood.%20India's%20burgeoning%20ties%20with%20key%20stakeholders%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20most%20remarkable%20foreign%20policy%20achievements%20of%20the%20Modi%20government.%20For%20a%20Prime%20Minister%20who%20is%20often%20only%20looked%20at%20through%20the%20prism%20of%20Hindu%20nationalism%2C%20building%20strong%20ties%20with%20the%20Arab%20states%20has%20resulted%20in%20New%20Delhi%20achieving%20a%20distinct%20clout%20in%20the%20region.%20Those%20who%20want%20to%20use%20the%20ideological%20lens%20often%20emphasize%20how%20Narendra%20Modi%20became%20the%20first%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20visit%20Israel%20and%20bring%20the%20relationship%20out%20into%20the%20open.%20But%20India-Israel%20ties%20had%20been%20growing%20steadily%20since%20the%20early%201990s.%20Modi%20simply%20brought%20it%20out%20of%20the%20closet.%20His%20real%20contribution%20is%20to%20make%20India's%20Arab%20partners%20recognize%20the%20need%20to%20build%20a%20relationship%20with%20India%20that%20can%20respond%20to%20the%20challenges%20of%20the%2021st%20century%2C%20instead%20of%20just%20being%20an%20extension%20of%20our%20religious%20heritage.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EModi's%20initial%20response%20to%20the%20attacks%20on%20Israel%20have%20generated%20a%20peculiar%20response%20in%20most%20quarters.%20His%20critics%20were%20rather%20too%20quick%20to%20point%20out%20what%20they%20saw%20a%20one-sided%20response.%20Why%20would%20he%20not%20talk%20about%20the%20Palestinians%2C%20they%20thundered.%20Others%20have%20seen%20in%20this%20a%20significant%20shift%20in%20India's%20traditionally%20balanced%20Middle%20East%20policy.%20But%20here%20was%20a%20leader%20responding%20to%20a%20vicious%20terror%20attack%20on%20a%20friendly%20nation.%20In%20that%20moment%2C%20expressing%20solidarity%20with%20Israel%20was%20the%20least%20that%20any%20Indian%20leader%20could%20have%20done.%20Imagine%2C%20after%20a%20terror%20attack%20on%20India%2C%20when%20Indian%20leaders%20seek%20solidarity%20from%20our%20friends%2C%20they%20being%20told%20that%20this%20is%20a%20response%20to%20New%20Delhi's%20own%20actions!%C2%A0India%20has%20been%20in%20such%20situations%20in%20the%20past%20and%20it%20knows%20that%20how%20it%20feels%20to%20fight%20terror%20alone.%20Modi's%20response%20was%20neither%20one-sided%20nor%20was%20it%20a%20significant%20shift%20in%20Indian%20policy.%20It%20was%20an%20expression%20of%20support%20to%20a%20friend%20that%20has%20always%20been%20there%20for%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20released%20its%20statement%20on%20the%20crisis%2C%20it%20made%20it%20perfectly%20clear%20that%20New%20Delhi%20views%20the%20strikes%20by%20Hamas%20on%20Israeli%20cities%20as%20%26quot%3Bterror%20attacks%2C%26quot%3B%20while%20reaffirming%20India's%20long-standing%20position%2C%20and%20advocating%20negotiations%20towards%20establishing%20a%20%26quot%3Bsovereign%2C%20independent%20and%20viable%26quot%3B%20state%20of%20Palestine%20living%20side-by-side%20at%20peace%20with%20Israel.%20India%20has%20maintained%20this%20position%20despite%20the%20pulls%20and%20pressures%20of%20changing%20regional%20dynamics.%20While%20Modi%20was%20indeed%20the%20first%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20visit%20Israel%2C%20he%20was%20also%20the%20first%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20visit%20the%20West%20Bank%20city%20of%20Ramallah%20in%20Palestine%20in%202018.%20For%20all%20the%20talk%20of%20supporting%20the%20Palestinian%20cause%2C%20no%20other%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20had%20made%20this%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20unfortunate%20that%20Congress%20Party's%20initial%20statement%20that%20did%20not%20mention%20the%20terror%20attacks%20by%20Hamas%20at%20all%20and%20gave%20the%20perception%20of%20there%20being%20a%20partisan%20divide%20on%20this%20issue%20in%20India.%20Though%20the%20Congress%20has%20since%20changed%20its%20position%20and%20denounced%20Hamas%2C%20for%20many%20around%20the%20world%20domestic%20polarisation%20in%20India%20became%20the%20primary%20prism%20to%20understand%20the%20Indian%20stand%20on%20the%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Indian%20approach%20towards%20the%20Middle%20East%20is%20increasingly%20being%20driven%20by%20the%20transformational%20changes%20being%20ushered%20in%20the%20Arab%20world%20and%20New%20Delhi's%20critical%20role%20in%20that%20order.%20The%20attacks%20by%20Hamas%20are%20aimed%20at%20dismantling%20the%20nascent%20shift%20in%20the%20region%2C%20which%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20change%20regional%20politics%20in%20fundamental%20ways.%20New%20Delhi%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20actors%20to%20recognize%20this%20shift%20and%20evolve%20its%20foreign%20policy%20accordingly%2C%20thereby%20moving%20beyond%20religion%20in%20defining%20the%20parameters%20of%20its%20engagement%20with%20regional%20stakeholders.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20many%20in%20India%20who%20are%20concerned%20that%20the%20country%20does%20not%20seem%20to%20be%20with%20the%20Global%20South%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20ongoing%20crisis.%20But%20it%20cannot%20be%20any%20other%20way%2C%20given%20the%20high%20stakes%20involved.%20India%20as%20one%20of%20the%20long-standing%20victims%20of%20terrorism%2C%20has%20often%20stood%20alone%20in%20challenging%20and%20questioning%20the%20world%20(even%20the%20West)%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20double%20standards%20on%20terrorism.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20tensions%20soar%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20Indian%20diplomacy%20will%20certainly%20be%20under%20pressure.%20But%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20region%2C%20this%20has%20always%20been%20a%20persistent%20challenge.%20What%20is%20new%20is%20New%20Delhi's%20desire%20to%20play%20a%20constructive%20and%20pegmatite%20role%20in%20the%20region%20in%20sync%20with%20evolving%20strategic%20realities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHarsh%20V.%20Pant%20is%20a%20Professor%20of%20International%20Relations%20at%20King's%20College%20London.%20He%20is%20Vice%20President%20-%20Studies%20and%20Foreign%20Policy%20at%20Observer%20Research%20Foundation%2C%20New%20Delhi.%20He%20is%20also%20the%20Director%20(Honorary)%20of%20the%20Delhi%20School%20of%20Transnational%20Affairs%20at%20Delhi%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697616300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F9cmv5j1_gaza-reuters_625x300_15_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fas-israel-hamas-crisis-escalates-indian-diplomacy-under-pressure-4491722%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Given%20India's%20growing%20stakes%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20it%20too%20can't%20remain%20immune%20to%20the%20reverberations%20from%20its%20extended%20neighbourhood.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fas-israel-hamas-crisis-escalates-indian-diplomacy-under-pressure-4491722%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Failed%20Gazan%20Rocket%20Or%20Israeli%20Strike%3F%20Hospital%20Tragedy%20Sparks%20Blame%20Game%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20at%20a%20hospital%20in%20Gaza%20on%20Tuesday%20has%20sparked%20a%20blame%20game%20between%20Israel%20and%20Palestine%2C%20with%20each%20side%20accusing%20the%20other%20of%20being%20responsible%20for%20the%20horrifying%20tragedy%2C%20which%20has%20left%20nearly%20500%20people%20dead.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20explosion%2C%20which%20came%20hours%20before%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20scheduled%20visit%20to%20Israel%2C%20has%20also%20caused%20an%20international%20furore%20and%20protests.%20US%20diplomatic%20efforts%20to%20drum%20up%20support%20for%20Israel%20have%20also%20been%20derailed%2C%20with%20Jordan%20announcing%20that%20Mr%20Biden's%20meeting%20in%20Amman%20on%20Wednesday%20with%20Jordan's%20King%20Abdullah%2C%20Egypt's%20President%20Abdel%20Fattah%20El-Sissi%20and%20Palestinian%20Authority%20President%20Mahmoud%20Abbas%20stands%20cancelled.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Murdered%20Their%20Own%20Children'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20the%20explosion%20ripped%20through%20the%20Al-Ahli%20Arab%20Hospital%20-%20which%20was%20one%20of%2020%20in%20northern%20Gaza%20facing%20evacuation%20after%20the%20Israeli%20military%20ordered%20civilians%20to%20move%20south%20last%20week%20-%20Hamas%20blamed%20Israel%20and%20said%20the%20tragedy%20was%20the%20result%20of%20an%20Israeli%20airstrike.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20Defense%20Forces%20(IDF)%20then%20began%20posting%20a%20series%20of%20videos%20claiming%20that%20a%20rocket%20aimed%20at%20the%20country%20had%20misfired%20at%20exactly%20the%20same%20time%20-%2018%3A59%20-%20as%20the%20hospital%20was%20hit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20also%20said%20that%20intelligence%20indicated%20that%20Islamic%20Jihad%2C%20a%20group%20allied%20with%20Hamas%2C%20was%20responsible%20for%20the%20%26quot%3Bfailed%20rocket%20launch%20which%20hit%20the%20hospital%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20analysis%20of%20IDF%20operational%20systems%20indicates%20that%20a%20barrage%20of%20rockets%20was%20fired%20by%20terrorists%20in%20Gaza%2C%20passing%20in%20close%20proximity%20to%20the%20Al%20Ahli%20hospital%20in%20Gaza%20at%20the%20time%20it%20was%20hit.%20Intelligence%20from%20multiple%20sources%20we%20have%20in%20our%20hands%20indicates%20that%20Islamic%20Jihad%20is%20responsible%20for%20the%20failed%20rocket%20launch%20which%20hit%20the%20hospital%20in%20Gaza%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Netanyahu%20posted%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20post%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20entire%20world%20should%20know%3A%20It%20was%20barbaric%20terrorists%20in%20Gaza%20that%20attacked%20the%20hospital%20in%20Gaza%2C%20and%20not%20the%20IDF.%20Those%20who%20brutally%20murdered%20our%20children%20also%20murder%20their%20own%20children.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDeleted%20Tweet%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20countered%20strongly%20by%20Palestinian%20Ambassador%20to%20the%20UN%2C%20Riyad%20Mansour%2C%20who%20called%20Mr%20Netanyahu%20a%20%26quot%3Bliar%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20that%20the%20Israeli%20military%20hit%20the%20hospital%20thinking%20that%20there%20was%20a%20Hamas%20base%20nearby.%20He%20also%20claimed%20that%20Mr%20Netanyahu's%20spokesperson%20had%20tweeted%20as%20much%2C%20and%20then%20deleted%20the%20tweet%2C%20and%20that%20the%20Israelis%20were%20now%20changing%20their%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20(Mr%20Netanyahu)%20is%20a%20liar.%20His%20digital%20spokesperson%20tweeted%20that%20Israel%20did%20the%20hit%20thinking%20that%20there%20was%20a%20base%20for%20Hamas%20around%20this%20hospital%2C%20and%20then%20he%20deleted%20that%20tweet.%20We%20have%20a%20copy%20of%20that%20tweet...%20Now%20they%20changed%20the%20story%20to%20try%20to%20blame%20the%20Palestinians%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Mansour%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20Israeli%20Army%20had%20called%20for%20the%20evacuation%20of%20hospitals%2C%20where%20many%20civilians%20in%20Gaza%20had%20been%20sheltering%20after%20their%20houses%20had%20been%20reduced%20to%20rubble%20in%20Israeli%20airstrikes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Israeli%20spokesperson%20of%20the%20Army%20made%20a%20statement%20in%20which%20he%20said%20evacuate%20the%20hospitals...%20%C2%A0Their%20intention%20is%20to%20evacuate%20or%20hospitals%20will%20be%20hit%20and%20they%20are%20responsible%20for%20that%20crime%20and%20they%20cannot%20fabricate%20stories%20to%20deal%20with%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Mansour%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIsrael%20Videos%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20least%203%2C000%20people%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20Gaza%20since%20the%20war%20began%20on%20October%207%20and%20Israel%20has%20been%20claiming%20that%20this%20was%20a%20result%20of%20Hamas%20using%20civilians%20as%20%26quot%3Bhuman%20shields%26quot%3B.%20Several%20posts%20by%20the%20handle%20of%20the%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20on%20X%20blamed%20Islamic%20Jihad%20for%20the%20explosion%20a