utm_campaign%3Demail-post%26r%3Dhzn2u%26utm_source%3Dsubstack%26utm_medium%3Demail%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3EThe%20India%20Cable%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%93%C2%A0a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%C2%A0The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20republished%20here.%20To%20subscribe%20to%20The%20India%20Cable%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Ftheindiacable.com%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3Eclick%20here%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20popular%20Kishore%20Kumar%20song%20from%20a%201983%20Hindi%20movie%20%3Cem%3EMohabbat%3C%2Fem%3E%20could%20be%20a%20lesson%20to%20arrogant%2C%20power-drunk%20political%20elites%20the%20world%20over%2C%20and%20would%20particularly%20apply%20to%20Israel%20and%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu.%20The%20song%20goes%3A%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EDahshat%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%3Cem%3Ese%20nahin%2C%20taqat%20se%20nahin%2C%20mohabbat%20se%20chalti%20hai%20duniya%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%20(The%20world%20cannot%20be%20run%20by%20terror%20or%20fear%2C%20but%20only%20by%20love.)%20It%20may%20sound%20utopian%2C%20but%20it%20is%20not%20far%20from%20the%20truth.%20Western%20nations%20led%20by%20the%20US%20have%20turned%20a%20blind%20eye%20to%20the%20events%20which%20led%20to%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20on%20Israel%20on%20October%207.%20True%2C%20there%20is%20no%20excuse%20for%20killing%20innocent%20civilians%2C%20women%20and%20children%2C%20whatever%20the%20provocation.%20But%20no%20one%20is%20caring%20to%20tell%20Netanyahu%20that%20violence%20begets%20violence%2C%20however%20weak%20the%20opponent%20may%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHaving%20beaten%20the%20Palestinians%20to%20submission%20for%20over%2075%20years%2C%20Zionist%20ideologues%20have%20brutally%20succeeded%20in%20their%20project.%20But%20a%20corrupt%20and%20dishonourable%20Netanyahu%20has%20managed%20to%20further%20humiliate%20and%20dehumanise%20the%20Palestinians%20in%20the%20name%20of%20a%20mythical%20war%20against%20them%20dating%20from%20the%20time%20of%20Abraham.%20This%20may%20sound%20somewhat%20familiar%20to%20Indians%20at%20the%20moment!%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20military%20is%20armed%20with%20deadly%20military%20spyware%20like%20Pegasus.%20They%20have%20the%20best%20equipment%20to%20keep%20an%20eye%20around%20the%20clock%20on%20the%20entire%20open%20prison%20called%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%20Yet%2C%20there%20was%20a%20colossal%20intelligence%20failure.%20The%20leading%20Israeli%20daily%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.haaretz.com%2Fisrael-news%2F2023-10-08%2Fty-article%2F.premium%2Fa-failure-of-all-systems-with-political-shock-waves-like-73%2F0000018b-0c06-dae3-a1cb-bd0f3be90000%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHaaretz%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20the%20other%20day%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20failure%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20intelligence%20and%20poor%20preparedness%20weren%E2%80%99t%20the%20only%20problems%20%E2%80%93%20it%20seems%20that%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20operational%20defensive%20conception%20in%20Gaza%20has%20shattered.%20Netanyahu%20will%20have%20to%20pay%20a%20political%20price%20for%20his%20Hamas%20policy%20after%20the%20war.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENetanyahu%20has%20ordered%20more%20than%20a%20million%20Gazans%20to%20migrate%20to%20the%20South%20if%20they%20care%20for%20their%20lives.%20Israeli%20forces%20are%20preparing%20to%20conquer%20northern%20Gaza%20and%20obliterate%20Hamas.%20Netanyahu%20wants%20a%20million%20people%20to%20vacate%20North%20Gaza%20in%2024%20hours%2C%20which%20the%20UN%20says%20is%20not%20only%20unfeasible%20but%20a%20violation%20of%20international%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20events%20unfolding%20are%20a%20reminder%20of%20the%20tragic%20consequences%20of%20Operation%20Blue%20Star%2C%20when%20the%20Indian%20military%20in%20June%201984%20tried%20to%20clear%20Jarnail%20Singh%20Bhindranwale%20and%20his%20armed%20militia%20out%20of%20the%20Golden%20Temple%20in%20Amritsar.%20The%20Indian%20army%20finally%20succeeded%2C%20but%20at%20what%20cost%20%E2%80%94%20Indira%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20assassination%20by%20her%20security%20guards%20and%20the%20killing%20of%20thousands%20of%20Sikhs%20in%20Delhi%20and%20elsewhere%20in%20north%20India%20in%20%E2%80%98retaliation%E2%80%99%20for%20her%20killing.%20The%20cycle%20of%20violence%20never%20ends.%20Who%20will%20tell%20Netanyahu%20this%3F%20Certainly%20not%20the%20Americans%20or%20Europeans.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20doubt%20that%20Israel%20has%20enough%20muscle%20and%20firepower%20to%20obliterate%20Palestinians%20from%20Gaza%2C%20the%20task%20for%20which%20the%20extreme%20right-wing%20has%20propped%20up%20Netanyahu%2C%20and%20never%20mind%20his%20gross%20corruption%20and%20authoritarian%20behaviour.%20Add%20to%20that%20the%20immediate%20replenishment%20of%20their%20arsenal%20by%20the%20US%20with%20tons%20of%20lethal%20armaments%2C%20to%20equip%20Netanyahu%20to%20wipe%20out%20Palestinians%20from%20whatever%20little%20is%20left%20of%20their%20enclave.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20Western%20leaders%20are%20with%20Netanyahu%20in%20this%20enterprise%2C%20widespread%20demonstrations%20are%20being%20held%20in%20almost%20all%20Western%20nations%20in%20support%20of%20the%20Palestinians%2C%20condemning%20Netanyahu%20and%20his%20apartheid%20policies.%20More%20pertinently%2C%20Israel%20has%20vowed%20to%20change%20the%20politics%20of%20the%20Middle%20East%20permanently.%20No%20one%20clearly%20knows%20what%20the%20Israeli%20government%20means%20by%20this.%20The%20Americans%20and%20Europeans%20have%20also%20not%20clarified%20what%20Netanyahu%E2%80%99s%20final%20objective%20is.%20There%20will%20be%20more%20clarity%20in%20the%20coming%20weeks%20as%20to%20where%20the%20dystopian%20world%20of%20Netanyahu%20is%20headed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFaraz%20Ahmad%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697614149000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18123957%2FF8aEEn1WYAAtWt0.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewi