0five-wicket%20win%20over%20Sri%20Lanka%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20they%20could%20come%20in%20and%20explain%20to%20us%20how%20it%20works%2C%20then%20sometimes%20we%20might%20(choose)%20not%20to%20refer%20or%20to%20refer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20Warner%20suggested%20that%20the%20ball-tracking%20did%20not%20match%20what%20he%20saw%20on%20the%20ground's%20replay%20screen%20after%20he%20called%20for%20the%20review.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20asked%20Joel%20(field%20umpire)%20when%20I%20was%20out%20there%20just%20what%20happened%2C%20why%20did%20he%20give%20it%20out.%20He%20said%20the%20ball%20was%20swinging%20back%20so%20to%20his%20credit%2C%20if%20he%20thinks%20that%20then%20that's%20why%20he's%20given%20a%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B(The%20ball)%20kept%20low%20and%20normally%20when%20something%20hits%20me%20on%20the%20leg%20on%20the%20outside%2C%20I%20know%20it's%20pretty%20much%20going%20down%20leg.%20So%20he%20(Wilson)%20said%20it%20was%20swinging%20back%2C%20(but)%20from%20my%20perspective%20on%20the%20replay%2C%20it%20wasn't%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20see%20the%20replay%20of%20how%20it%20unfolded%20you%20get%20a%20little%20bit%20annoyed%2C%20(but)%20that's%20out%20of%20our%20control.%26quot%3B%20Warner%20also%20felt%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report%2C%20that%20ball-tracking%20verdicts%20were%20%26quot%3Btaking%20a%20lot%20longer%20than%20what%20it%20would%20be%20in%20Australia%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Decision%20Review%20System%20was%20introduced%20in%202008%2C%20ahead%20of%20Warner's%20international%20debut%20in%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20moment%2C%20we%20seem%20to%20be%20waiting%20for%20(ball-tracking)%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Warner.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20as%20a%20player%20you%20get%20more%20frustrated%20because%20you%20think%3A%20'did%20they%20line%20it%20up%2C%20what's%20the%20impact%20points%2C%