%2C%20there%20are%20two%20likely%20changes%20this%20time%20%E2%80%93%20there%20will%20be%20no%20deadline%2C%20and%20organic%20export%20will%20not%20be%20exempted%20from%20restriction%2C%20sources%20told%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20restriction%20will%20halt%20shipments%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fmarkets%2Fcommodities%2Findia-set-ban-sugar-exports-first-time-7-years-2023-08-23%2F%5C%22%3Efirst%20time%20in%20seven%20years.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20restricted%20the%20amount%20of%20exports%20during%202022-23%20as%20well%2C%20allowing%20mills%20to%20export%20only%206.1%20million%20tonnes%20of%20sugar%20after%20letting%20them%20sell%20a%20record%2011.1%20million%20tonnes%20the%20season%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20news%20agency%20Reuters%20in%20August%2C%20a%20government%20source%20who%20asked%20not%20to%20be%20named%20in%20line%20with%20official%20rules%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20primary%20focus%20is%20to%20fulfill%20local%20sugar%20requirements%20and%20produce%20ethanol%20from%20surplus%20sugarcane.%20For%20the%20upcoming%20season%2C%20we%20will%20not%20have%20enough%20sugar%20to%20allocate%20for%20export%20quotas.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThough%20it%20is%20not%20a%20ban%2C%20it%20has%20the%20same%20meaning%20if%20permits%20are%20not%20issued%20for%20export.%20However%2C%20an%20early%20announcement%20will%20help%20mills%20plan%20how%20much%20sugarcane%20to%20be%20diverted%20to%20make%20sugar%20and%20how%20much%20for%20ethanol%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Feconomy%2Fagri-business%2Fgovt-to-prohibit-sugar-export-to-protect-domestic-market%2Farticle67429716.ece%5C%22%3Ean%20industry%20expert%20said.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697613610000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F26103523%2Fsugar-485055_1280.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire