%20continues%20its%20efforts%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20October%207%20massacre%20by%20Hamas%2C%20Jews%20are%20now%20more%20political%20than%20ever%20in%20their%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20days%20of%20Moses%2C%20when%20they%20escaped%20the%20wrath%20of%20the%20Egyptian%20kingdom%20in%20popular%20imagination%2C%20to%20Hitler's%20Holocaust%2C%20Jews%20have%20faced%20many%20a%20catastrophe%2C%20and%20have%20bounced%20back%20each%20time.%20Today%2C%20Jews%20are%20a%20very%20strong%20community%2C%20and%20they%20have%20a%20state%20to%20call%20their%20own.%20It%20is%20ironic%20that%20a%20community%2C%20stateless%20and%20without%20geographical%20boundaries%20for%20centuries%2C%20is%20now%20refusing%20to%20understand%20the%20plight%20of%20Palestinians%20and%20is%20determined%20to%20render%20them%20stateless.%20There%20is%20no%20doubt%20that%20Israel%20is%20the%20'promised%20land'%2C%20which%20is%20at%20the%20core%20of%20their%20belief%20system.%20But%20their%20unwillingness%20to%20coexist%20with%20Palestinians%20is%20another%20great%20mystery%20of%20modern%20times.%20Is%20it%20because%20Jews%20now%20believe%20they%20are%20the%20'chosen%20ones'%20with%20the%20'promised%20land'%2C%20and%20that%20they%20should%20keep%20it%2C%20preserve%20it%20and%20pay%20any%20price%3F%20That%20they%20should%20not%20lose%20it%2C%20and%20punish%20anyone%20who%2C%20by%20any%20stretch%20of%20imagination%2C%20is%20trying%20to%20leave%20them%20stateless%20again%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20present%20crisis%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20has%20to%20be%20seen%20in%20civilisational%20terms.%20This%20is%20the%20land%20that%20gave%20birth%20to%20three%20religions%20-%20Judaism%2C%20Christianity%20and%20Islam%20-%20and%20all%20three%20were%20inspired%20by%20Abraham.%20As%20Johnson%20says%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20Bible%20presents%20him%20as%20the%20immediate%20ancestor%20of%20the%20Hebrew%20people%20and%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20nation%3B%20he%20is%20also%20the%20supreme%20example%20of%20the%20good%20and%20just%20man.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJews%20and%20Palestinians%20were%20rivals%20even%20then.%20It%20is%20no%20accident%20of%20history%20that%20even%20in%20modern%20times%2C%20before%20the%20Second%20World%20War%2C%20there%20was%20debate%20on%20where%20Jews%20would%20settle%2C%20and%20out%20of%20all%20the%20options%2C%20the%20land%20of%20Palestine%20was%20chosen%20to%20create%20a%20Jewish%20state%20that%20is%20Israel.%20This%20was%20the%20land%20where%20the%20Jews%20had%20started%20migrating%20to%20since%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%2020th%20century.%20With%20the%20promise%20of%20the%20Balfour%20declaration%20in%201917%2C%20the%20pace%20of%20immigration%20magnified%20many%20times.%20Finally%2C%20in%20May%201948%2C%20they%20were%20given%2056%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20land%20and%20the%20Palestinians%2C%20who%20were%20the%20original%20inhabitants%2C%20got%20only%2044%20per%20cent.%20Thus%20started%20the%20new%20history.%20The%20oppressed%20of%20history%20became%20the%20new%20oppressors.%20The%20victims%20are%20the%20new%20rulers.%20Unless%20we%20understand%20this%20paradox%2C%20it%20will%20be%20difficult%20to%20understand%20the%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20doubt%20that%20no%20community%20has%20suffered%20more%20than%20the%20Jews.%20If%20the%20Holocaust%20is%20so%20deeply%20identified%20with%20Hitler%2C%20then%20Jews%20are%20inseparable%20from%20this%20darkest%20chapter%20in%20history.%20But%20now%2C%20the%20same%20Jews%20are%20allegedly%20out%20to%20homeless%20those%20who%20were%20the%20real%20owners%20of%20the%20land%20on%20which%20they%20have%20set%20up%20their%20state.%20There%20is%20no%20doubt%20that%20the%20Hamas'%20attack%20was%20unpardonable%2C%20a%20terrorist%20act%2C%20barbaric.%20However%2C%20if%20Israel%20and%20its%20leadership%20believe%20they%20are%20justified%20in%20avenging%20the%20attack%20by%20acting%20like%20Hamas%2C%20they%20are%20grossly%20mistaken.%20Israel%20is%20a%20modern%20state%20and%20as%20a%20state%2C%20it%20can't%20behave%20the%20way%20Hamas%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20state%20cannot%20behave%20like%20a%20terrorist%20organisation.%20It%20is%20bound%20by%20rules%20and%20laws.%20It%20has%20to%20differentiate%20between%20terrorists%20and%20people.%20Just%20because%20Hamas%20was%20chosen%20by%20the%20local%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza%20Strip%20does%20not%20make%20them%20accessories%20to%20the%20barbaric%20act.%20The%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20government%20cannot%20punish%20people%20for%20the%20acts%20of%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAsking%201.1%20million%20people%20of%20North%20Gaza%20to%20evacuate%20in%2024%20hours%20and%20move%20to%20south%20Gaza%20is%20equally%20unpardonable%3B%20shutting%20off%20their%20water%20and%20electricity%20is%20no%20less%20barbaric%2C%20and%20if%20the%20international%20community%20fails%20to%20convince%20the%20Israeli%20government%2C%20they%20are%20failing%20in%20their%20duty%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael%20is%20a%20tiny%20state%20with%20a%20world%20class%20intelligence%20network%20and%20military%2C%20and%20is%20very%20robustly%20supported%20by%20the%20most%20powerful%20state%20in%20the%20world%2C%20the%20US.%20It%20shares%20its%20geographical%20boundaries%20with%20hostile%20neighbours.%20Since%20the%20day%20it%20declared%20its%20independence%2C%20it%20has%20faced%20three%20full-fledged%20wars%20and%20relentless%20terrorist%20acts.%20Because%20of%20civilisational%20reasons%2C%20it%20is%20perpetually%20in%20a%20heightened%20state%20of%20anxiety.%20This%20anxiety%20will%20not%20ebb%20if%20there%20are%20leaders%20like%20Netanyahu%20and%20ultra%20nationalist%20coalition%20partners%20in%20his%20cabinet.%20I%20know%20that%20one%20has%20to%20distinguish%20between%20common%20Jews%20and%20Zionists%3B%20no%20Jew%20in%20Israel%20and%20outside%20is%20a%20Palestine%20hater.%20Many%20want%20to%20live%20in%20harmony%20with%20Arabs%20within%20Israel%20and%20outside.%20Since%20the%20state%20is%20controlled%20by%20Zionists%2C%20however%2C%20it%20is%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20leaders%20to%20understand%20that%20a%20state%20can't%20live%20in%20fear%20and%20uncertainty.%20If%20Israel%20has%20to%20live%20in%20peace%2C%20then%20it%20has%20to%20first%20recognise%20the%20fact%20that%20Palestinian%20also%20have%20a%20right%20to%20exist%20and%20that%20they%20can't%20be%20punished%20for%20demanding%20their%20legitimate%20right%20to%20a%20state%20of%20their%20own%2C%20where%20they%20are%20the%20masters%20of%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Oslo%20accord%20was%20the%20first%20step%20in%20that%20direction.%20It%20devised%20the%20two-state%20theory%2C%20which%20meant%20that%20Israel%20and%20Palestine%20are%20two%20different%20nations%20and%20should%20live%20contiguously%20as%20two%20states.%20Unfortunately%2C%20Israel%20is%20not%20willing%20to%20implement%20the%20accord.%20The%20PLO%20(Palestinian%20Liberation%20Organisation)%2C%20led%20by%20Left-leaning%20Yasser%20Arafat%2C%20who%20had%20grudgingly%20accepted%20the%20formula%2C%20was%20marginalised%20by%20the%20rise%20of%20Hamas.%20Israel%20was%20its%20creator.%20Paradoxically%2C%20Hamas%2C%20an%20Islamist%20organisation%20that%20never%20accepted%20the%20existence%20of%20Israel%2C%20is%20its%20new%20scourge.%20The%20Israeli%20leadership%20has%20to%20admit%20that%20sooner%20than%20later%20this%20game%20has%20to%20end.%20As%20a%20state%20it%20has%20to%20accept%20the%20reality%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20it%20has%20to%20accept%20the%20legitimate%20right%20of%20Palestinians.%20It%20has%20to%20realise%20that%20war%20has%20failed%20to%20yield%20any%20solution%20in%20last%2075%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20it%20has%20the%20option%20to%20enter%20Gaza%2C%20annex%20the%20land%20and%20leave%20Palestinians%20homeless%2C%20or%20turn%20this%20catastrophe%20into%20an%20opportunity%2C%20show%20magnanimity%2C%20and%20make%20an%20offer%20that%20is%20acceptable%20to%20them%20and%20live%20in%20peace.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20I%20will%20quote%20what%20Paul%20Johnson%20said%20about%20Jews%2C%20%26quot%3BNo%20people%20have%20been%20more%20fertile%20in%20enriching%20poverty%20or%20humanising%20wealth%2C%20or%20in%20turning%20misfortune%20to%20creative%20account.%26quot%3B%20Will%20they%20turn%20the%20present%20misfortune%20into%20a%20creative%20account%20once%20again%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Ashutosh%20is%20author%20of%20'Hindu%20Rashtra'%20and%20Editor%2C%20satyahindi.com.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697612940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F784tv3ig_khan-yunis-gaza-afp_625x300_14_October_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fisrael-cannot-respond-to-hamas-like-hamas-4491671%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20Israel%20continues%20its%20efforts%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20October%207%20massacre%20by%20Hamas%2C%20Jews%20are%20now%20more%20political%20than%20ever%20in%20their%20history.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fisrael-cannot-respond-to-hamas-like-hamas-4491671%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fisrael-cannot-respond-to-hamas-like-hamas-4491671%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fisrael-cannot-respond-to-hamas-like-hamas-4491671%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cambodian%20opposition%20figure%20Thach%20Setha%20jailed%20for%20three%20years%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697612898000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104519240%2Cimgsize-36244.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fcambodian-opposition-figure-thach-setha-jailed-for-three-years%2Farticleshow%2F104519088.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%