20sides%20blamed%20each%20other%20for%20the%20explosion.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAll%20Palestinian%20groups%20in%20Gaza%20blame%20Israel%20for%20the%20attack%2C%20calling%20it%20a%20massacre%20and%20a%20war%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJordan%20rushed%20to%20cancel%20the%20planned%20summit%20on%20Wednesday%20with%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20Egyptian%20President%20Abdel%20Fattah%20el-Sisi.%20Palestinian%20leader%20Mahmoud%20Abbas%20earlier%20withdrew%20from%20the%20meeting%20due%20to%20the%20attack%20on%20the%20hospital%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20placed%20the%20blame%20on%20Islamic%20Jihad%2C%20a%20militant%20group%20in%20Gaza.%20In%20a%20statement%20on%20X%20(former%20Twitter)%20he%20wrote%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20entire%20world%20should%20know%20-%20it%20was%20the%20barbaric%20terrorists%20in%20Gaza%20that%20attacked%20the%20hospital%2C%20and%20not%20the%20IDF.%20Those%20who%20brutally%20murdered%20our%20children%20also%20murdered%20their%20own%20children.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIDF%20spokesman%20Daniel%20Hagari%20also%20put%20the%20blame%20on%20Islamic%20Jihad.%20In%20a%20public%20video%20statement%20late%20Tuesday%20he%20said%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can%20confirm%20that%20an%20analysis%20of%20the%20IDF%20operational%20systems%20indicates%20that%20a%20barrage%20of%20rockets%20was%20fired%20by%20terrorists%20in%20Gaza%2C%20passing%20in%20close%20proximity%20to%20the%20Al-Ahli%20hospital%20in%20Gaza%20at%20the%20time%20it%20was%20hit%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUN%20Secretary-General%20Antonio%20Guterres%20strongly%20condemned%20the%20deadly%20hospital%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20horrified%20by%20the%20killing%20of%20hundreds%20of%20Palestinian%20civilians%20in%20a%20strike%20on%20a%20hospital%20in%20Gaza%20today%2C%20which%20I%20strongly%20condemn%2C%26quot%3B%20Guterres%20said%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20heart%20is%20with%20the%20families%20of%20the%20victims.%20Hospitals%20and%20medical%20personnel%20are%20protected%20under%20international%20humanitarian%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EArab%20representatives%20at%20the%20UN%20have%20called%20for%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas.%20The%20Palestinian%20UN%20ambassador%20urges%20the%20international%20society%20to%20stop%20Israel's%20%26quot%3Bcrimes%20against%20humanity%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20spokesman%20for%20Palestinian%20President%20Mahmoud%20Abbas%20called%20the%20attack%20on%20the%20hospital%20an%20act%20of%20%26quot%3Bgenocide%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20%26quot%3Bhumanitarian%20catastrophe%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20social%20media%2C%20Turkish%20President%20Recep%20Tayyip%20Erdogan%20denounced%20the%20attack%20and%20blamed%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHitting%20a%20hospital%20containing%20women%2C%20children%20and%20innocent%20civilians%20is%20the%20latest%20example%20of%20Israel's%20attacks%20devoid%20of%20the%20most%20basic%20human%20values%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20invite%20all%20humanity%20to%20take%20action%20to%20stop%20this%20unprecedented%20brutality%20in%20Gaza.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELate%20Tuesday%20night%2C%20spontaneous%20demonstrations%20against%20Israel%20were%20held%20in%20several%20Middle%20Eastern%20capitals.%20The%20Lebanese%20Hezbollah%20militia%20responded%20to%20the%20hospital%20attack%20by%20declaring%20Wednesday%20%26quot%3Ba%20day%20of%20unprecedented%20anger%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETension%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hezbollah%20has%20been%20growing%20the%20past%20week.%20Tuesday%20was%20no%20exception.%20Hezbollah%20fired%20at%20least%20six%20anti-tank%20missiles%20into%20Israeli%20cities%20close%20to%20the%20border%2C%20and%20rockets%20hit%20the%20Israeli%20city%20of%20Kiryat%20Shemona.%20Israel%20retaliated%20by%20targeting%20Hezbollah%20positions%20in%20the%20southern%20parts%20of%20Lebanon.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20State%20Department%20raised%20the%20threat%20level%20for%20Lebanon%20in%20its%20travel%20advisory%20for%20the%20Middle%20Eastern%20country%20to%20level%204%20last%20night.%20This%20is%20the%20highest%20possible%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20family%20members%20of%20the%20official%20US%20staff%20working%20in%20Lebanon%20can%20now%20leave%20the%20country.%20The%20same%20applies%20to%20some%20government%20employees%20at%20the%20US%20embassy%20in%20the%20country's%20capital%2C%20Beirut.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Gaza%2C%20more%20than%203%2C000%20Palestinians%20have%20been%20killed%20since%20the%20fighting%20began%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20Hamas'%20attack%20on%20Israel%20on%20Saturday%2C%20October%207.%20Some%201%2C400%20Israelis%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20humanitarian%20crisis%20inside%20Gaza%20is%20escalating.%20Hospitals%20are%20no%20longer%20able%20to%20treat%20the%20rising%20number%20of%20wounded.%20Although%20a%20humanitarian%20aid%20convoy%20for%20Gaza%20has%20arrived%20at%20the%20Egyptian%20side%20of%20the%20Rafah%20crossing%2C%20Israel%20has%20still%20not%20allowed%20the%20convoy%20to%20enter%20Gaza.%20More%20than%20100%20trucks%20with%20food%2C%20water%20and%20medicine%20are%20waiting%20on%20the%20Egyptian%20side%20of%20the%20border%2C%20and%20there%20is%20no%20confirmation%20about%20when%20the%20convoy%20will%20be%20allowed%20into%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20arriving%20in%20Israel%20on%20Wednesday%20President%20Biden%20is%20expected%20to%20take%20part%20in%20a%20meeting%20with%20the%20Israeli%20war%20cabinet%20at%20the%20headquarters%20in%20Tel%20Aviv.%20Biden%20is%20also%20expected%20to%20demand%20that%20Israel%20allow%20emergency%20aid%20to%20enter%20Gaza.%20Earlier%20this%20week%2C%20Israel%20rejected%20a%20plea%20from%20US%20and%20Egypt%20to%20make%20aid%20to%20Gaza%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELarge%20numbers%20of%20Palestinians%20are%20still%20heading%20to%20the%20southern%20parts%20of%20Gaza%20after%20Israel%20ordered%20them%20to%20leave%20the%20northern%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAn%20estimated%206%2C00%2C000%20Palestinians%20have%20fled%20the%20northern%20areas%20out%20of%20a%20total%201.1%20million%20in%20these%20areas.%20More%20than%20one%20million%20residents%20have%20been%20displaced%20in%20Gaza%2C%20which%20has%20a%20population%20of%202.3%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Danish%20branch%20of%20Doctors%20Without%20Borders%20evacuated%20its%20staff%20from%20the%20northern%20parts%20of%20Gaza%20on%20Tuesday.%20In%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20aid%20organization%20said%20it%20had%20moved%20its%20staff%20to%20the%20southern%20part%20of%20Gaza%20due%20to%20the%20dangerous%20conditions%20in%20the%20northern%20parts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20phone%20conversation%20with%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%2C%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20declared%20he%20was%20willing%20to%20help%20prevent%20a%20humanitarian%20disaster%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20phone%20call%20with%20Biden%2C%20Egyptian%20President%20Abdel%20Fattah%20el-Sisi%20warned%20that%20an%20escalation%20of%20the%20conflict%20in%20Gaza%20could%20threaten%20regional%20security.%20The%20Egyptian%20President%20has%20rejected%20the%20idea%20of%20letting%20Palestinians%20from%20Gaza%20flee%20to%20safety%20in%20the%20Egyptian%20peninsula%20of%20Sinai.%20Scores%20of%20Palestinians%20are%20sleeping%20at%20the%20Rafah%20border%20area%20between%20Gaza%20and%20Egypt%2C%20waiting%20for%20the%20border%20crossing%20to%20be%20opened.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Allan%20Sorensen%20is%20the%20Middle%20East%20correspondent%20for%20the%20Danish%20daily%20newspaper%20Kristeligt%20Dagblad.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697612460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fngbm75sc_daily-despatch_625x300_