20health%20facilities%20are%20bombed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20targeting%20of%20hospitals%20is%20a%20war%20crime%20under%20the%20Geneva%20Conventions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20day%20the%20WHO%20issued%20this%20statement%2C%20which%20also%20called%20on%20Israel%20to%20rescind%20its%20evacuation%20order%2C%20the%20al-Ahli%20hospital%20was%20hit%20by%20Israeli%20rocket%20fire%2C%20injuring%20four%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.archbishopofcanterbury.org%2Fnews%2Fnews-and-statements%2Fgaza-hospitals-are-facing-catastrophe-says-archbishop-canterbury%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20statement%20by%20the%20Archbishop%20of%20Canterbury%2C%20head%20of%20the%20Anglican%20church%3A%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHospitals%20and%20patients%20in%20Gaza%20are%20in%20grave%20danger.%20The%20seriously%20ill%20and%20injured%20patients%20at%20the%20Anglican-run%20Ahli%20Hospital%20%E2%80%93%20and%20other%20healthcare%20facilities%20in%20northern%20Gaza%20%E2%80%93%20cannot%20be%20safely%20evacuated.%20They%20are%20running%20low%20on%20medical%20supplies.%20They%20are%20facing%20catastrophe.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Ahli%20Hospital%20was%20hit%20by%20Israeli%20rocket%20fire%20last%20night%2C%20with%20four%20staff%20injured%20in%20the%20blast.%20Other%20hospitals%20have%20also%20been%20hit.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20appeal%20for%20the%20evacuation%20order%20on%20hospitals%20in%20northern%20Gaza%20to%20be%20reversed%20%E2%80%93%20and%20for%20health%20facilities%2C%20health%20workers%2C%20patients%20and%20civilians%20to%20be%20protected.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20evil%20and%20barbaric%20terror%20attacks%20on%20Israelis%20by%20Hamas%20were%20a%20blasphemous%20outrage.%20But%20the%20civilians%20of%20Gaza%20are%20not%20responsible%20for%20the%20crimes%20of%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPlease%20continue%20to%20pray%20for%20all%20innocent%20people%2C%20Israeli%20and%20Palestinian%2C%20who%20are%20caught%20up%20in%20the%20terrible%20violence%20in%20the%20Holy%20Land.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98War%20crime%20is%20a%20specific%20term.%20The%20WHO%20can%E2%80%99t%20determine%20that%E2%80%99%3A%20WHO%20representative%20at%20presser%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20issuing%20the%20statement%2C%20the%20UN%20health%20body%20in%20a%20hurriedly%20convened%20presser%20said%20it%20was%20still%20trying%20to%20ascertain%20the%20full%20scale%20of%20the%20loss%20of%20human%20life%20and%20other%20resources%20in%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERichard%20Peeperkorn%2C%20WHO%20Representative%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98occupied%20Palestinian%20territory%20%5Bthis%20is%20WHO%20nomenclature%5D%2C%20said%20he%20had%20seen%20media%20reports%20saying%20the%20number%20of%20dead%20in%20the%20attack%20could%20range%20from%20200-800.%20%E2%80%9CI%20find%20it%20difficult%20to%20speculate%20%5Bthe%20number%20of%20dead%5D%20but%20it%20will%20be%20verified%20soon.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20WHO%20officials%20did%20not%20say%20how%20many%20patients%20were%20undergoing%20treatment%20in%20the%20hospital%20at%20the%20time%20of%20attack%20but%20all%20media%20reports%20suggest%20that%20all%20hospitals%20are%20overwhelmed%20in%20Gaza.%20The%20WHO%20officials%20did%20say%20in%20the%20presser%20that%20%E2%80%98thousands%20and%20thousands%E2%80%99%20of%20internally%20displaced%20people%20have%20taken%20refuge%20in%20the%20hospitals%20since%20they%20considered%20it%20a%20place%20that%20was%20immune%20to%20any%20military%20attack.%20And%2C%20al-Alhi%20hospital%20was%20no%20exception%20to%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20international%20NGO%20MSF%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FMSF%2Fstatus%2F1714363238240973125%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eput%20out%20a%20tweet%20by%20one%20of%20its%20doctors%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20al-Ahli%20hospital%20following%20the%20bombing%3A%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20operating%20in%20the%20hospital%2C%20there%20was%20a%20strong%20explosion%2C%20and%20the%20ceiling%20fell%20on%20the%20operating%20room.%20This%20is%20a%20massacre%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Ghassan%20Abu%20Sittah%2C%20MSF%20doctor%20in%20Gaza.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESeveral%20non-profit%20organisations%20working%20in%20healthcare%20have%20condemned%20the%20attack.%20US-based%20%E2%80%98Physicians%20for%20Human%20Rights%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20is%20also%20a%20recipient%20of%20the%20Nobel%20Peace%20Prize%2C%20called%20it%20the%20%E2%80%98deadliest%20attack%20on%20healthcare%20across%20any%20conflict%20in%20the%20world%20in%20recent%20years%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20call%20for%20an%20impartial%2C%20independent%2C%20international%20investigation%20into%20the%20Al-Ahli%20al-Arabi%20Hospital%20strike.%20The%20perpetrators%20must%20be%20held%20to%20account%20for%20this%20serious%20violation%20of%20international%20law%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said%20in%20a%20statement%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMedicines%20Sans%20Frontiers%20(MSF)%20said%20it%20was%20horrified%20by%20the%20attack.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20operating%20in%20the%20hospital%2C%20there%20was%20a%20strong%20explosion%2C%20and%20the%20ceiling%20fell%20on%20the%20operating%20room.%20This%20is%20a%20massacre%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Ghassan%20Abu%20Sittah%2C%20an%20MSF%20doctor%20in%20Gaza%2C%20has%20been%20quoted%20in%20its%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20bloodshed%20must%20stop.%20Enough%20is%20enough%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECalling%20the%20attack%20%E2%80%98totally%20unacceptable%E2%80%99%2C%20Volker%20T%C3%BCrk%2C%20UN%20High%20Commissioner%20for%20Human%20Rights%2C%20said%2C%20once%20again%2C%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20section%20of%20people%20were%20targeted.%20He%20demanded%20the%20guilty%20must%20be%20held%20accountable%20and%20gave%20a%20call%20to%20%E2%80%98all%20States%20with%20influence%E2%80%99%20to%20do%20%E2%80%98everything%20in%20their%20power%20to%20bring%20an%20end%20to%20this%20horrendous%20situation%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHours%20after%20the%20bombing%2C%20doctors%20from%20the%20al-Ahli%20hospital%20held%20a%20press%20conference%20amidst%20the%20bodies%20of%20some%20of%20the%20hundreds%20of%20victims%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20bombing%20on%20October%2017.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20the%20current%20conflict%20started%2C%203%2C000%20people%20had%20been%20killed%20in%20Palestine%2C%20according%20to%20the%20WHO.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20WHO%20officials%20said%20before%20the%20attack%20on%20al-Ahli%20hospital%2C%20there%20had%20been%20115%20attacks%20on%20%E2%80%98health%E2%80%99%20in%20Palestine%20with%2051%20of%20them%20in%20Gaza%20and%20the%20rest%20in%20the%20West%20Bank.%20As%20many%20as%2015%20healthcare%20workers%20had%20been%20killed%20on%20the%20line%20of%20duty%20while%2027%20others%20were%20injured.%20As%20many%20as%2024%20health%20facilities%20were%20affected%20and%20damaged%20in%20Gaza%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20WHO%20officials%20refused%20to%20say%20if%20they%20had%20any%20information%20whether%20the%20attack%20was%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20Israeli%20military%20or%20it%20was%20a%20case%20of%20Palestinian%20Islamic%20Jihad%2C%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20information%20that%20they%20could%20have%20gathered%20from%20their%20team%20on%20the%20grounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%E2%80%99s%20for%20criminal%20investigation%20to%20find%20out%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Mike%20Ryan%2C%20executive%20director%20of%20WHO%E2%80%99s%20Health%20Emergencies%20Programme.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20WHO%20can%E2%80%99t%20determine%20the%20origin%20or%20the%20trajectory%20of%20the%20weapon.%20We%20are%20here%20to%20condemn%20the%20attack%20of%20this%20ferocity..%20of%20this%20scale%20of%20violence%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20agency%20experts%20also%20did%20not%20say%20whether%20they%20would%20like%20to%20classify%20the%20attack%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98war%20crime%E2%80%99%2C%20while%20replying%20to%20a%20journalist%E2%80%99s%20query%2C%20even%20though%20they%20condemned%20it%20very%20strongly.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWar%20crime%20is%20a%20specific%20term.%20The%20WHO%20can%E2%80%99t%20determine%20that%E2%80%A6the%20causation%20or%20attribution%20is%20a%20vast%20call%20for%20the%20WHO%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ryan%20said%2C%20while%20adding%20that%20international%20humanitarian%20law%20calls%20for%20protection%20of%20healthcare%20and%20healthcare%20workers.%20And%2C%20any%20such%20attack%20was%20a%20violation%20of%20international%20humanitarian%20laws%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20WHO%20officials%20expressed%20%E2%80%98frustration%E2%80%99%20with%20the%20fact%20that%20truckloads%20of%20essential%20supplies%2C%20including%20medicine%2C%20equipment%2C%20food%20and%20other%20such%20materials%20were%20lying%20idle%20at%20Egypt%E2%80%99s%20border%20while%20the%20people%20in%20Gaza%20are%20suffering%20badly%20due%20to%20scarcity%20of%20these%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAsked%20to%20clarify%20if%20the%20problem%20was%20from%20Israeli%20side%20or%20Egyptian%2C%20Richard%20Brennan%2C%20Regional%20Emergency%20Director%20of%20WHO%E2%80%99s%20Eastern%20Mediterranean%20Regional%20Office%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Rafah%20crossing%20remains%20closed%20at%20this%20stage%20and%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20lot%20of%20aid%20that%20has%20built%20up%20on%20the%20Egyptian%20side%E2%80%A6We%E2%80%99re%20ready%20to%20go%20as%20soon%20as%20there%20is%20an%20opening.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERyan%20added%20it%20was%20not%20just%20about%20the%20Rafah%20crossing.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20what%20happens%20on%20the%20far%20side%20of%20that%20crossing.%20Because%20delivering%20aid%20to%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20crossing%20is%20not%20good%20enough%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fembed%3Fpb%3D!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3411.0089965298594!2d34.256848775600666!3d31.248174274339785!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x14fd93842067f5cd%253A0x330d09c6cad7ca73!2sRafah%2520Crossing!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1697598388592!5m2!1sen!2sin%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22450%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20people%20are%20scattered%20all%20over%20Gaza.%20The%20hospitals%20are%20scattered%20all%20over%20Gaza.%20There%20needs%20to%20be%20safe%20access%20to%20those%20facilities%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ryan%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20why%20the%20supplies%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20transported%20further%20from%20the%20Egyptian%20side%20into%20Gaza%2C%20Brennan%20replied%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20different%20dynamics%20going%20on.%20We%20understand%20that.%20We%20know%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20lot%20of%20diplomacy%20here.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20senior%20UN%20officials%20were%20arriving%20at%20Egypt%E2%80%99s%20capital%20Cario%20that%20night%20and%20the%20next%20day%20he%20hoped%20they%20would%20be%20able%20to%20negotiate%20with%20all%20the%20relevant%20parties%20to%20get%20the%20opening%20going%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EState%20of%20healthcare%20centres%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20state%20of%20affairs%20of%20healthcare%20centres%2C%20Peeperkorn%20said%20more%20than%2060%25%20of%20primary%20health%20centres%20were%20not%20functioning%20in%20Palestine.%20As%20far%20as%20hospitals%20are%20concerned%2C%2030%20out%20of%2034%20were%20functioning%20but%20with%20fast-dwindling%20supplies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20medicines%20required%20not%20just%20for%20surgeries%20and%20trauma%20were%20nearly%20exhausted%20but%20even%20basic%20things%20such%20as%20cleaning%20materials%20for%20hospital%20wards.%20Therefore%2C%20hospitals%20are%20now%20reporting%20cases%20of%20infections%20arising%20out%20of%20unhygienic%20conditions%20in%20the%20wards.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20patients%20who%20suffer%20from%20diseases%20such%20as%20cardiovascular%2C%20oncology%20and%20other%20such%20ailments%20are%20not%20able%20to%20find%20medicines%20anymore.%20It%20had%20become%20difficult%20for%20hospitals%20even%20to%20cater%20to%20pregnant%20women.%20The%20blood%20banks%20are%20also%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20being%20dried%20up%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWorse%2C%20the%20hospitals%20may%20run%20out%20of%20fuel%20in%20a%20day%20or%20so%2C%20Peepkorn%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20people%20have%20been%20displaced%2C%20the%20WHO%20officials%20also%20feared%20outbreak%20of%20communicable%20diseases.%20Lack%20of%20drinking%20water%20and%20sanitation%20services%20would%20only%20exacerbate%20the%20health%20issues%20of%20the%20people%20living%20in%20Gaza%2C%20Peepkorn%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAll%20officials%20reversal%20of%20evacuation%20order%20given%20by%20Israel.%20Even%20in%20most%20advanced%20countries%2C%20evacuation%20of%20patients%20admitted%20with%20serious%20injuries%20was%20impossible%2C%20Ryan%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20it%20was%20impossible%20to%20imagine%20doing%20it%20in%20a%20conflict-ridden%20situation%20in%20which%20incessant%20attacks%20and%20bombings%20were%20taking%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20WHO%20had%20called%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20evacuation%20order%20a%20death%20sentence%20for%20patients%20undergoing%20treatment%20in%20the%20hospitals.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERyan%20also%20said%20the%20WHO%20was%20in%20touch%20with%20Israel%20and%20had%20offered%20medical%20assistance.%20But%20since%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20medical%20system%20was%20highly%20advanced%2C%20the%20country%20did%20not%20feel%20the%20need%20to%20take%20any%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENote%3A%20This%20article%2C%20first%20published%20at%205.38%20am%20on%20October%2018%2C%202023%2C%20was%20updated%20and%20republished%20at%208%20am%20on%20the%20same%20day%20with%20details%20on%20the%20WHO%20presser.