mers%20at%20Rs%202%2C500%20per%20quintal%20and%20wheat%20at%20Rs%202%2C600%20per%20quintal%20with%20the%20goal%20of%20increasing%20it%20to%20Rs%2C%203%2C000%20per%20quintal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENath%2C%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20CM%20face%20in%20the%20state%2C%20said%20the%20party%20would%20make%20efforts%20to%20get%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20its%20own%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%20team.%20The%20more%20than%201%2C200%20promises%20made%20by%20the%20Congress%20in%20its%20vachan%20patra%20touched%2059%20major%20themes%20and%20229%20pointers.%20This%20included%20the%20promise%20to%20provide%20the%20educated%20unemployed%20youth%20with%20Rs%2015%2C00-3%2C000%20per%20month%20and%20Rs%201%2C500%20to%20every%20woman%20per%20month%20under%20the%20Nari%20Samman%20Yojana%20and%20Rs%201.01%20support%20sum%20for%20the%20marriage%20of%20girls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20manifesto%20reiterated%20some%20of%20the%20social%20welfare%20promises%20already%20made%20by%20the%20Congress%20to%20voters%20in%20its%20public%20rallies%20following%20its%20thumping%20success%20in%20Karnataka%20earlier%20this%20year.%20Under%20the%20Congress%20government%2C%20LPG%20cylinders%20would%20cost%20Rs%20500%20and%20not%20Rs%201%2C000%3B%20electricity%20bills%20for%20100%20units%20of%20power%20would%20be%20waived%20off%2C%20while%20it%20would%20be%20halved%20for%20200%20units%3B%20the%20Old%20Pension%20Scheme%20could%20be%20implemented%20and%20farm%20loans%20would%20be%20waived%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20its%2018%20years%20in%20power%2C%20the%20BJP%20ruined%20every%20institution%20and%20system.%20MP%E2%80%99s%20economy%20was%20ruined.%20The%20youth%20are%20unemployed%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Nath.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F17192201%2FF8oD1roWcAAOHje.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F17192201%2FF8oD1roWcAAOHje.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F17192201%2FF8oD1roWcAAOHje-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F17192201%2FF8oD1roWcAAOHje-1024x683.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-680509%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EKamal%20Nath%2C%20Digvijay%20Singh%20and%20others%20release%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20manifesto%20for%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20on%20October%2017.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40OfficeofKNath%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20rival%20and%20present%20chief%20minister%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20was%20quick%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20promises%2C%20dismissing%20them%20as%20lies.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20%3Cem%3Emaha%20jhooth%20patra%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Five%20years%20ago%2C%20Kamal%20Nath%20made%20900%20promises%20but%20did%20not%20implement%20even%20nine%20of%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Chouhan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20just%20a%20month%20left%20for%20voting%20in%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20assembly%20election%2C%20Chouhan%20is%20at%20an%20unfamiliar%20crossroads.%20Though%20he%20has%20been%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20government%20in%20the%20state%20since%202005%2C%20a%20remarkable%20feat%20by%20all%20means%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fshivraj-chouhan-position-bommai-defeat-bjp-madhya-pradesh%5C%22%3Euncertainty%20looms%20large%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20his%20own%20political%20future.%20Will%20Chouhan%20return%20as%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20CM%20even%20if%20the%20party%20wins%2C%20is%20the%20biggest%20question%20on%20the%20minds%20of%20political%20observers%2C%20as%20the%20central%20Indian%20state%20with%20230%20assembly%20seats%20heads%20to%20another%20tight%20battle%20%E2%80%93%20just%20like%20the%20one%20it%20witnessed%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChouhan%20lost%20power%20in%20that%20election%20and%20was%20in%20the%20opposition%20for%20a%20little%20over%20a%20year%20before%20returning%20as%20CM%20after%20almost%20two%20dozen%20Congress%20MLAs%2C%20led%20by%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%2C%20defected%20and%20toppled%20the%20Kamal%20Nath-led%20government.%20In%202023%2C%20Chouhan%2C%20once%20seen%20as%20a%20possible%20prime%20ministerial%20candidate%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20seems%20to%20be%20fighting%20two%20battles%3A%20one%20for%20the%20BJP%20in%20its%20quest%20to%20keep%20the%20Congress%20out%20and%20the%20second%2C%20a%20lone%20one%2C%20for%20his%20own%20political%20relevance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20BJP%20finally%20announced%20Chouhan%E2%80%99s%20name%20in%20its%20fourth%20list%20of%20candidates%20last%20week%2C%20after%20agonising%20speculation%20over%20the%20possibility%20of%20him%20being%20dropped%2C%20the%20party%20is%20yet%20to%20officially%20declare%20him%20as%20the%20CM%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20challenged%20by%20an%20ascendant%20and%20confident%20Congress%2C%20led%20by%20its%20state%20president%20and%20former%20chief%20minister%20Kamal%20Nath%2C%20who%20has%20been%20leading%20from%20the%20front%20in%20anchoring%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20strategy%2C%20incorporating%20rebels%20from%20the%20saffron%20camp%20and%20responding%20to%20his%20opponents%20with%20wit.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20the%20Congress%20made%20a%20remarkable%20jump%20from%2050-odd%20seats%20in%202013%20to%20emerge%20as%20the%20largest%20party%20in%20the%20MP%20assembly.%20The%20party%20won%20114%20seats%20but%20fell%20just%20short%20of%20the%20golden%20halfway%20mark%20by%20just%20two%20seats.%20The%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20tally%20dropped%20to%20109%2C%20even%20though%20the%20saffron%20party%20had%20a%20marginally%20higher%20vote%20count%20and%20vote%20percentage.%20With%20the%20support%20of%20two%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20MLAs%2C%20a%20Samajwadi%20Party%20MLA%20and%20four%20independent%20winners%2C%20the%20Congress%20formed%20a%20government%20with%20Kamal%20Nath%20as%20CM.%20Though%20the%20BJP%20managed%20to%20wrest%20back%20control%20of%20the%20state%20after%20the%20rebellion%20by%20the%20Congress%20MLAs%2C%20its%20government%20headed%20by%20Chouhan%20post-2020%20was%20already%20running%20against%20popular%20mandate.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChouhan%E2%80%99s%20popularity%20and%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20position%20only%20seem%20to%20have%20become%20weaker%20since%20then%2C%20as%20the%20continuous%20rebellions%20and%20the%20saffron%20party%E2%80%99s%20reluctance%20to%20put%20faith%20in%20Chouhan%20as%20its%20face%2C%20indicate.%20Chouhan%E2%80%99s%20attempts%20to%20add%20a%20darker%20shade%20of%20Hindutva%20to%20his%20well-cultivated%20image%20of%20%E2%80%9Cmama%E2%80%9D%20through%20the%20use%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fkhargone-ram-navami-violence-bulldozer%5C%22%3Ebulldozers%20to%20demolish%20property%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20targets%20and%20shriller%20rhetoric%20have%20done%20little%20to%20redeem%20his%20position.%20In%20recent%20months%2C%20he%20has%20tried%20to%20control%20the%20damage%20by%20announcing%20new%20schemes%20and%20measures%20like%20the%20Ladli%20Behna%20and%2035%25%20reservation%20for%20women%20in%20jobs%2C%20even%20this%20has%20not%20been%20enough%20for%20the%20BJP%20to%20declare%20him%20as%20their%20official%20CM%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20BJP%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-experimental-strategy-union-ministers-mps-assembly-elections-modi%5C%22%3Efielding%3C%2Fa%3E%20three%20Union%20ministers%2C%20four%20MPs%20and%20a%20national%20general%20secretary%20in%20the%20Assembly%20election%20%E2%80%93%20many%20of%20them%20possible%20contenders%20for%20the%20top%20post%20%E2%80%93%20Chouhan%E2%80%99s%20position%20increasingly%20looks%20precarious.%20At%20a%20recent%20rally%2C%20Chouhan%20made%20an%20emotional%20appeal%20to%20the%20voters.%20%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20run%20the%20government.%20I%20run%20a%20family.%20You%20will%20not%20find%20a%20brother%20like%20this.%20You%20will%20miss%20me%20when%20I%20am%20gone%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EK.K.%20Mishra%2C%20chairman%20of%20the%20media%20department%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%20MP%2C%20is%20dismissive%20of%20Chouhan%E2%80%99s%20prospects.%20%E2%80%9CShivraj%20Singh%3Cem%3Eji%20thay%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Kamal%20Nath%3Cem%3Eji%20hain%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0(Shivraj%20Singh%20is%20past.%20Kamal%20Nath%20is%20the%20present%20and%20the%20future)%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mishra%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CChouhan%20has%20not%20been%20declared%20the%20CM%20candidate%20by%20the%20BJP.%20The%20BJP%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20consider%20him%20a%20face%2C%20so%20why%20shall%20we%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChouhan%E2%80%99s%20future%20is%20not%20the%20only%20issue%20dominating%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20this%20season.%20The%20election%20result%20would%20also%20be%20a%20commentary%20on%20Union%20minister%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%2C%20who%20had%20rebelled%20against%20the%20Congress%20to%20join%20the%20BJP%20and%20help%20the%20latter%20form%20the%20government.%20In%20recent%20months%2C%20several%20Scindia%20loyalists%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmaharaj-doesnt-have-power-in-the-bjp-scindias-clout-wanes-as-loyalists-return-to-congress%5C%22%3Ereturned%20to%20the%20Congress%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Moreover%2C%20many%20BJP%20leaders%20and%20legislators%20past%20and%20present%20have%20also%20shifted%20ranks%20to%20the%20Congress%20due%20to%20the%20disquiet%20caused%20in%20the%20saffron%20camp%20by%20the%20entry%20of%20Scindia%20loyalists%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20northern%20belts%20of%20the%20Gwalior-Chambal%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2F06155547%2Fscindia-bjp.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2F06155547%2Fscindia-bjp.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2F06155547%2Fscindia-bjp-300x150.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2F06155547%2Fscindia-bjp-1024x512.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2F06155547%2Fscindia-bjp-800x400.jpg%20800w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-490703%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EJyotiraditya%20Scindia.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40JM_Scindia%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20fighting%20this%20election%20with%20a%20multi-pronged%20approach%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20its%20star%20campaigner%2C%20as%20expected.%20The%20party%20is%20trying%20to%20sell%20the%20idea%20that%20it%20has%20rid%20the%20state%20of%20its%20%E2%80%98BIMARU%E2%80%99%20image%20over%20the%20last%20two%20decades.%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%2C%20recently%20launched%20a%20report%20card%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20achievements%20in%20the%20state%20from%202003%20to%202023%20under%20the%20Gareeb%20Kalyan%20Mahaabhiyan.%20%E2%80%9COnce%20written%20off%2C%20the%20state%20is%20now%20in%20the%20list%20of%20the%20prosperous%20and%20happy%20states%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Shah%2C%20listing%20achievements%20in%20water%20supply%2C%20electricity%2C%20education%2C%20roads%2C%20economy%2C%20irrigation%2C%20law%20and%20order%2C%20health%20and%20other%20indices.%20He%20said%20that%20since%20the%20BJP%20came%20to%20power%20in%20MP%20in%202003%2C%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20per%20capita%20income%20had%20increased%20from%20Rs%2011%2C700%20to%20Rs%201.40%20lakh.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20election%20is%20to%20completely%20free%20people%20from%20poverty%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Shah.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhy-congresss-obc-politics-in-madhya-pradesh-is-to-shivraj-singh-chauhans-benefit%5C%22%3EThe%20BJP%20High%20Command%20Is%20Alarmed%20by%20MP%20CM%20Shivraj%20Blowing%20Hot%20and%20Cold%20on%20His%20Future%20Plans%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECongress%20on%20the%20front%20foot%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKamal%20Nath%20has%20taken%20the%20BJP%20and%20Chouhan%20head-on.%20He%20has%20released%20an%20%3Cem%3Eaarop%20patra%3C%2Fem%3E%20(chargesheet)%20of%20alleged%20corruption%20and%20scams%20under%20the%20Chouhan%20government%20%E2%80%93%20a%20document%20titled%20%E2%80%9CGhotala%20hi%20Ghotala%E2%80%94Ghotala%20seth%2C%2050%25%20commission%20rate.%E2%80%9D%20In%20a%20letter%20addressed%20to%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20youth%20on%20October%2011%2C%20Nath%20said%20that%20in%20the%2018%20years%20that%20the%20BJP%20was%20in%20power%2C%20it%20pushed%20its%20level%20of%20education%20and%20skills%20to%20new%20lows%2C%20leading%20to%20unemployment.%20%E2%80%9CToday%20MP%20identifies%20as%20a%20state%20with%20recruitment%20scams%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Nath.%20Apart%20from%20questioning%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20record%20on%20corruption%2C%20jobs%2C%20inflation%20and%20law%20and%20order%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20announced%20its%20own%20slew%20of%20welfare%20promises%2C%20including%20waiving%20off%20farmer%20debt%2C%20100%20units%20of%20free%20power%2C%20Rs%201%2C500%20monthly%20stipend%20for%20women%20and%20free%20education%20till%20Class%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECaste%20has%20also%20taken%20centre-stage%20in%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20this%20election.%20The%20party%20has%20emphatically%20promised%20to%20conduct%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fafter-bihar-cong-govt-in-rajasthan-to-conduct-caste-survey-makes-it-main-agenda-in-madhya-pradesh%5C%22%3Ecaste%20survey%20in%20the%20state%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20along%20the%20lines%20of%20the%20one%20conducted%20in%20Bihar%2C%20if%20it%20comes%20to%20power.%20This%2C%20along%20with%20the%20infusion%20of%20backward%20caste%20and%20Bahujan%20political%20rhetoric%20in%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20campaign%2C%20looks%20to%20pose%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20BJP%20in%20its%20self-avowed%20perception%20game%20as%20the%20party%20that%20best%20represents%20the%20backward%20castes.%20Chouhan%20is%20an%20OBC%2C%20while%20Modi%20has%20on%20several%20occasions%20referred%20to%20his%20caste%20identity%20to%20woo%20the%20sizeable%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20recent%20rally%20in%20Shahdol%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20described%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20national%20caste%20census%20as%20an%20%E2%80%9CX-ray%E2%80%9D%20that%20would%20determine%20the%20status%20of%20OBCs%2C%20Dalits%20and%20tribal%20communities%20and%20determine%20how%20much%20representation%20they%20should%20be%20provided.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20recent%20speeches%20in%20MP%2C%20Modi%20sought%20to%20label%20the%20opposition%20as%20working%20against%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20nation%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Hindu%20community.%20On%20September%2014%2C%20amid%20a%20controversy%20over%20Sanatan%20Dharma%2C%20Modi%20accused%20the%20Congress-led%20INDIA%20bloc%20of%20running%20a%20hidden%20agenda%20of%20%E2%80%9Cdisintegrating%E2%80%9D%20Sanatan%20Dharma.%20On%20September%2025%2C%20the%20PM%20accused%20the%20Congress%20of%20outsourcing%20everything%2C%20from%20slogans%20to%20policies%2C%20to%20%E2%80%9Csome%20Urban%20Naxals.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F03105424%2FScreenshot-2023-10-03-at-10.53.5.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F03105424%2FScreenshot-2023-10-03-at-10.53.5.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F03105424%2FScreenshot-2023-10-03-at-10.53.5-300x154.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F03105424%2FScreenshot-2023-10-03-at-10.53.5-1024x525.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-677981%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22615%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPM%20Narendra%20Modi%20at%20Gwalior%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20on%20October%202.%20Photo%3A%20Video%20screengrab%2FX%2F%40narendramodi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20all%20its%20dynamics%2C%20the%20contest%20looks%20tight%2C%20say%20political%20observers%2C%20who%20are%20finding%20it%20difficult%20to%20call%20which%20way%20it%20may%20swing.%20In%202018%2C%20too%2C%20the%20margins%20were%20quite%20thin.%20With%20the%20BSP%20contesting%20in%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20tribal-based%20Gondwana%20Ganatantra%20Party%20and%20the%20SP-Congress%20alliance%20seeming%20unlikely%20in%20the%20state%20despite%20being%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20it%20is%20a%20direct%20battle%20between%20the%20two%20main%20parties%20%E2%80%93%20the%20BJP%20and%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYatindra%20Singh%20Sisodia%2C%20director%20of%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Institute%20of%20Social%20Science%20Research%20in%20Ujjain%2C%20says%20there%20is%20definite%20fatigue%20and%20anti-incumbency%20against%20the%20Shivraj-led%20BJP%20government.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20Congress%20has%20not%20made%20any%20big%20blunder%20as%20far%20as%20the%20narrative%20goes%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sisodia%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EObservers%20also%20point%20out%20that%20in%20this%20election%2C%20it%20is%20the%20BJP%20and%20not%20the%20Congress%20that%20is%20grappling%20with%20internal%20strife%20and%20factionalism.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESisodia%20feels%20the%20performance%20of%20the%20parties%20in%20the%2047%20seats%20reserved%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20communities%20will%20be%20crucial%20in%20the%20end%2C%20as%20he%20feels%20the%20two%20parties%20are%20likely%20to%20retain%20their%20support%20base%20or%20numbers%20in%20the%20other%20regions.%20More%20than%2021%25%20of%20MP%E2%80%99s%20population%20belongs%20to%20tribal%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWill%20Kamal%20Nath%20finally%20end%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20long%20run%20in%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20largest%20states%3F%20More%20importantly%2C%20will%20he%20get%20a%20mandate%20strong%20enough%20to%20rule%20for%20the%20full%20term%3F%20These%20are%20questions%20that%20optimistic%20Congress%20supporters%20will%20be%20thinking%20about.%20For%20Chouhan%2C%20there%20is%20more%20at%20stake%20this%20time%2C%20primarily%20his%20political%20stature.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMishra%2C%20the%20Congress%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20media%20department%20chairman%2C%20says%20that%20this%20election%20season%2C%20there%20has%20hardly%20been%20any%20protest%20against%20the%20party%20by%20disgruntled%20workers%20or%20leaders.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20there%20have%20been%20demonstrations%20and%20stone-pelting%20incidents%20outside%20the%20BJP%20office%2C%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20the%20first%20election%20where%20we%20have%20no%20dispute%20over%20the%20leadership%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Mishra.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20are%20sure%20to%20have%20a%20big%20psychological%20impact%20on%20both%20the%20Congress%20and%20BJP%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20image%20of%20the%20major%20players%2C%20especially%20Modi%2C%20when%20attention%20shifts%20to%20the%202024%20general%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697596220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F17180205%2Fcollage.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmadhya-pradesh-polls-ascendant-congress-disgrunt