ed%20the%20blast%3B%20Israel%20and%20Palestinian%20groups%20both%20blamed%20each%20other%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20explosion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGraphic%20photos%20published%20by%20wire%20services%20appeared%20to%20show%20wounded%20Palestinians%20after%20the%20attack.%20Gazan%20health%20officials%20said%20that%20at%20least%20500%20people%20had%20died%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20bombing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Palestinian%20Health%20Ministry%20said%20on%20Facebook%20Tuesday%20that%20Israeli%20forces%20had%20attacked%20the%20al-Ahli%20hospital%20in%20Gaza%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhich%20shelters%20displaced%20people%20from%20the%20ongoing%20aggression%20on%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20spokesperson%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20%26quot%3Ban%20enemy%20rocket%20barrage%20was%20carried%20out%20towards%20Israel%2C%20which%20passed%20through%20the%20vicinity%20of%20the%20hospital%20when%20it%20was%20hit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENetanyahu%20also%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnetanyahu%2Fstatus%2F1714371254617022641%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eposted%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20%26quot%3Ban%20analysis%20of%20IDF%20operational%20systems%20indicates%20that%20a%20barrage%20of%20rockets%20was%20fired%20by%20terrorists%20in%20Gaza%2C%20passing%20in%20close%20proximity%20to%20the%20Al%20Ahli%20hospital%20in%20Gaza%20at%20the%20time%20it%20was%20hit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIntelligence%20from%20multiple%20sources%20we%20have%20in%20our%20hands%20indicates%20that%20Islamic%20Jihad%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20extremist%20group%20operating%20in%20Gaza%2C%20%26quot%3Bis%20responsible%20for%20the%20failed%20rocket%20launch%20which%20hit%20the%20hospital%20in%20Gaza%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Islamic%20Jihad%20denied%20the%20claim%2C%20saying%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20The%20Times%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere%20were%20no%20operations