ns.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20reports%20of%20protests%20from%20the%20Vidhyadhar%20Nagar%20constituency%20where%20the%20BJP%20has%20announced%20the%20candidature%20of%20Rajsamand%20MP%20Diya%20Kumari%20instead%20of%20Narpat%20Singh%20Rajvi%2C%20the%20son-in%20law%20of%20former%20chief%20minister%2C%20vice%20president%20of%20India%20and%20BJP%20stalwart%2C%20the%20late%20Bhairon%20Singh%20Shekhawat.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20a%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20central%20leadership%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fdenied-tickets-rajasthan-bjp-leaders-revolt-to-fight-against-official-nominees%2Farticleshow%2F104411182.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cupset%20at%20the%20brewing%20mutiny%20in%20the%20state%20unit%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20defeat%20in%20Karnataka%20came%20despite%20%E2%80%93%20or%20because%20of%20%E2%80%93%20its%20confidence%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98central%E2%80%99%20push%2C%20setting%20aside%20local%20leaders%20and%20factors.%20The%20loss%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20assembly%20polls%2C%20despite%20being%20party%20president%20J.P.%20Nadda%E2%80%99s%20home%20state%2C%20also%20would%20be%20looming%20large%20on%20its%20calculations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMPs%20as%20MLA%20candidates%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20announced%20MP%20Rajyavardhan%20Singh%20Rathore%20as%20its%20candidate%20for%20Jhotwara%20assembly%20seat.%20In%20this%20seat%2C%20supporters%20of%20former%20minister%20Rajpal%20Singh%20Shekhawat%20are%20said%20to%20have%20shown%20black%20flags%20to%20Rathore%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Felections%2Frajasthan-assembly-polls-2023%2Fstory%2Fbjp-candid