nancial%20viability%20and%20not%20become%20debt%20burdens%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20NSA%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20absence%20of%20direct%20land%20access%20between%20Central%20Asia%20and%20India%20is%20an%20anomaly%2C%20he%20said%2C%20which%20is%20a%20result%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Cconscious%20policy%20of%20denial%20by%20a%20particular%20country%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20Pakistan.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20situation%20is%20not%20only%20self-defeating%20for%20this%20country%20but%20it%20also%20reduces%20the%20collective%20well-being%20of%20the%20entire%20region%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20NSA%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDoval%20said%20that%20terrorism%20in%20all%20its%20forms%20and%20manifestations%20continues%20to%20constitute%20one%20of%20the%20most%20serious%20threats%20to%20international%20peace%20and%20security%20and%20that%20any%20act%20of%20terrorism%2C%20regardless%20of%20its%20motivation%20or%20cause%2C%20is%20unjustifiable.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20meeting%20is%20being%20held%20when%20the%20world%20is%20witnessing%20great%20challenges%2C%20adding%20that%20dialogue%20is%20the%20only%20answer%20to%20settling%20difference%20and%20disputes.%20%E2%80%9CDiplomacy%20must%20be%20at%20the%20Centre%20of%20all%20conflict%20resolution%20initiatives%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20NSA%20also%20offered%20fully%20funded%20capacity%20building%20programmes%20in%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20areas%20to%20the%20participating%20nations%20such%20as%20access%20to%20the%20technology%20of%20the%20United%20Payment%20Interface%20(UPI).%20He%20proposed%20a%20partnership%20in%20rare%20earth%20and%20strategic%20minerals.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Afghanistan%2C%20he%20said%20the%20situtation%20remains%20a%20cause%20of%20concern%20and%20the%20immediate%20priorities%20should%20be%20providing%20humanitarian%20assistance%20and%20ensuring%20the%20formation%20of%20a%20truly%20inclusive%20and%20representative%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20%E2%80%8Bthe%20strongest%20bond%20between%20Indian%20and%20Central%20Asia%20is%20the%20extensive%20cultural%20linkage%20and%20people-to-people%20ties.%20India%20will%20organise%20a%20seminar%20in%20India%20between%20leading%20scholars%20and%20ulemas%20from%20India%20and%20the%20Central%20Asian%20countries%2C%20Doval%20added.%20This%20will%20facilitate%20a%20deeper%20understanding%20of%20the%20history%20and%20context%20of%20Islam%20and%20its%20role%20in%20fostering%20peaceful%20coexistence%20and%20social%20harmony%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20complicated%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20national%20security%20advisers%20or%20secretaries%20of%20the%20National%20Security%20Councils%20of%20the%20Republic%20of%20India%2C%20the%20Republic%20of%20Kazakhstan%2C%20the%20Kyrgyz%20Republic%2C%20the%20Republic%20of%20Tajikistan%20and%20the%20Republic%20of%20Uzbekistan%20participated%20in%20the%20meeting.%20Turkmenistan%20was%20represented%20by%20the%20Embassy%20in%20Astana.%E2%80%8B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20Second%20Meeting%20of%20the%20India-Central%20Asia%20NSAs%2C%20with%20the%20first%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fafghanistan-terror-groups-ajit-doval%5C%22%3Eheld%20in%20New%20Delhi%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20December%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697561651000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F17221748%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-17-at-9.26.06-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fdoval-slams-pakistan-for-blocking-indias-land-access-to-central-asia%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Speaking%20at%20a%20conclave%20of%20national%20security%20advisors%20of%20India%20and%20Central%20Asian%20countries%2C%20he%20said%20the%20denial%20of%20direct%20access%20by%20Pakistan%20is%20not%20only%20self-defeating%20but%20also%20reduces%20the%20collective%20well-being%20of%20the%20entire%20region.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplom