th%20two%20doctors%20who%20ran%20the%20Indore-based%20hospital%20to%20join%20the%20franchise%20for%20which%20over%20Rs%2016%20crore%20was%20paid.%20The%20Indore%20hospital%20allegedly%20started%20violating%20the%20terms%20of%20the%20agreement%20which%20resulted%20in%20a%20dispute%20and%20Dr%20Agarwal%E2%80%99s%20wanted%20their%20money%20back%20and%20the%20termination%20of%20the%20agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20appointed%20an%20arbitrator%20to%20negotiate%20a%20settlement%2C%20and%20the%20arbitrator%20in%20an%20interim%20injunction%20asked%20the%20Indore-based%20hospital%20to%20deposit%20Rs%2016.43%20crore%20within%20four%20weeks.%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20dispute%2C%20the%20promoters%20of%20Dr%20Agarwal%E2%80%99s%20started%20getting%20messages%20and%20calls%20from%20Tiwari%20to%20forget%20the%20alleged%20dues%20and%20settle%20the%20matter%20with%20the%20doctors%20running%20the%20Indore%20hospital%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20PTI%20report%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20second%20time%20in%20less%20than%20100%20days%20that%20Maayank%20Tiwari%20has%20posed%20as%20a%20top%20PMO%20official.%20In%20June%2C%20he%20threatened%20a%20trustee%20of%20a%20private%20university%20in%20Vadodara%20and%20was%20tried%20to%20force%20a%20prestigious%20school%20to%20grant%20admission%20to%20two%20children%20who%20he%20claimed%20were%20his%20friend%E2%80%99s%20children.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20he%20spelt%20his%20name%20as%20Mayank.%20In%20the%20latest%20case%2C%20he%20has%20added%20an%20%E2%80%9Ca%E2%80%9D%20to%20his%20first%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20trustee%20of%20the%20school%20became%20suspicious%2C%20he%20alerted%20the%20police.%20The%20Gujarat%20police%20arrested%20Tiwari%20in%20June%20and%20said%20that%20was%20charging%20money%20for%20admissions%20and%20posing%20as%20a%20PMO%20official%20to%20threaten%20schools%20and%20college%20owners.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20exploits%20were%20minor%20compared%20to%20Kiran%20Patel%2C%20an%20Ahmedabad%20reside