9%2FWhatsApp-Image-2019-09-23-at-10.07.35.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20After%20the%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20account%20of%20Hindus%20for%20Human%20Rights%20was%20withheld%20in%20India%2C%20the%20nonprofit%20organisation%20said%20on%20Monday%2C%20October%2016%2C%20that%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20is%20%E2%80%9Cscared%20of%20a%20movement%20of%20progressive%20Hindus%20and%20their%20supporters%20speaking%20up%20to%20save%20Indian%20democracy%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20X%20account%20of%20Hindus%20for%20Human%20Rights%20and%20its%20partner%2C%20the%20Indian%20American%20Muslim%20Council%20(IAMC)%2C%20was%20withheld%20early%20on%20October%2014%20%E2%80%9Cin%20response%20to%20a%20legal%20demand%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20organisation%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release%20that%20the%20move%20shows%20that%20its%20%E2%80%9Ctruth-telling%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cconstant%20insistence%20on%20justice%E2%80%9D%20have%20become%20a%20thorn%20in%20the%20BJP-led%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%E2%80%99s%20clear%20is%20that%20there%20is%20a%20coordinated%20plan%20of%20transnational%20repression%20by%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20assisted%20by%20their%20eager%20partners%20in%20the%20diaspora%20%E2%80%93%20and%20their%20action%20against%20us%20may%20well%20represent%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20massive%20clamp%20down%20of%20anti-Modi%20voices%20prior%20to%20the%202024%20elections%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20press%20release%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20vowed%20not%20to%20be%20silence%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20movement%20against%20Hindutva%20will%20continue.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20separate%20statement%2C%20IAMC%20said%20that%20Elon%20Musk%20is%20%E2%80%9Cworking%20hand%20in%20glove%20with%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20authoritarian%20regime%E2%80%9D%20to%20block%20a%20US-based%20organisation%20and%20that%20X%20is%20%E2%80%9Caccelerating%20the%20suppression%20of%20free%20expression%20and%20democracy%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20suspensions%20are%20part%20of%20the%20Indian%20government%E2%80%99s%20broader%20crackdown%20on%20critical%20voices%2C%20IAMC%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20raids%20on%20NewsClick%2C%20the%20arrest%20of%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%20and%20giving%20the%20sanction%20for%20prosecution%20of%20writer-activist%20Arundhati%20Roy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERead%20both%20the%20press%20releases%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Modi%20Government%20Is%20Trying%20to%20Silence%20Us%20and%20We%20Will%20Fight%20Back%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWashington%20D.C.%20Monday%20October%2016%2C%202023%3A%20The%20Modi%20government%20is%20attempting%20to%20silence%20our%20voice%20by%20shutting%20down%20our%20Twitter%20account%20in%20India%20in%20collusion%20with%20Elon%20Musk%E2%80%99s%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20October%2014th%2C%20we%20learnt%20that%20X%20had%20%E2%80%9Cwithheld%E2%80%9D%20our%20Twitter%20account%20in%20India%2C%20%E2%80%9Cin%20response%20to%20a%20legal%20demand%2C%E2%80%9D%20presumably%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20India.%20Our%20ally%2C%20Indian%20American%20Muslim%20Council%E2%80%99s%20Twitter%20account%20has%20also%20been%20%E2%80%9Cwithheld%E2%80%9D%20similarly.%20There%20was%20no%20prior%20intimation%20by%20X%2C%20nor%20does%20it%20have%20an%20appeal%20process%20for%20this%20type%20of%20suspension%2C%20except%20in%20a%20court%20of%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20no%20idea%20why%20we%20have%20been%20shut%20down%2C%20but%20we%20can%20take%20a%20guess%3A%20The%20mighty%20Modi%20raj%20is%20scared%20of%20a%20movement%20of%20progressive%20Hindus%20and%20their%20supporters%20speaking%20up%20to%20save%20Indian%20democracy.%20Their%20action%20shows%20that%20our%20truth-telling%2C%20our%20constant%20insistence%20on%20justice%2C%20have%20become%20a%20thorn%20in%20their%20side.%20The%20truth%20frightens%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20clear%20is%20that%20there%20is%20a%20coordinated%20plan%20of%20transnational%20repression%20by%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20assisted%20by%20their%20eager%20partners%20in%20the%20diaspora%20%E2%80%93%20and%20their%20action%20against%20us%20may%20well%20represent%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20massive%20clamp%20down%20of%20anti-Modi%20voices%20prior%20to%20the%202024%20elections%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20our%20case%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFirst%20came%20the%20SLAPP%20lawsuit%20by%20the%20Hindu%20American%20Foundation%20(HAF)%20in%20May%202021%20against%20our%20co-founders.%20It%20failed%20to%20intimidate%20and%20silence%20us%20and%20the%20case%20was%20dismissed.%20Then%20came%20incessant%20trolling%20following%20the%20Dismantling%20Global%20Hindutva%20conference%20in%20September%202021%2C%20in%20which%20we%20had%20participated%20as%20practicing%20Hindus.%20We%20responded%20in%20kind%20and%20debunked%20the%20narrative%20that%20the%20conference%20was%20Hinduphobic.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20visit%20to%20the%20United%20States%20in%20May%202023%20came%20a%20shameful%20display%20of%20hubris%20and%20hype%20by%20a%20Union%20Minister%20in%20the%20Modi%20cabinet%2C%20claiming%20on%20national%20TV%20that%20there%20was%20a%20conspiracy%20among%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20George%20Soros%2C%20and%20our%20co-founder%20Sunita%20to%20destroy%20India.%20That%20failed%20to%20gain%20traction%20and%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20increased%20our%20following.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20now%20this!!%20Using%20their%20pal%20Elon%20Musk%20to%20shut%20down%20the%20only%20voice%20of%20progressive%20Hindus%2C%20which%20is%20speaking%20out%20against%20the%20danger%20of%20Hindutva%20ideology%20and%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20anti-minority%20actions%2C%20which%20run%20counter%20to%20the%20basic%20values%20of%20Hinduism.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMuch%20as%20they%20try%2C%20we%20will%20not%20be%20silenced%20or%20stopped%2C%20like%20a%20river%20flows%20on%20in%20spite%20of%20boulders%20in%20the%20way%2C%20finding%20its%20way%20around.%20As%20long%20as%20people%20like%20Umar%20Khalid%2C%20Teesta%20Setalvad%2C%20Harsh%20Mander%2C%20Arundhati%20Roy%2C%20Newsclick%2C%20Amnesty%20India%20%E2%80%A6..%20as%20long%20as%20brave%20defenders%20of%20Indian%20democracy%20are%20continuing%20to%20fight%2C%20we%20will%20stand%20with%20them.%20The%20resistance%20movement%20against%20Hindutva%20will%20grow%20like%20a%20tidal%20wave%20and%20engulf%20the%20hatred.%20That%20day%20will%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20second%20freedom%20struggle%20for%20India.%20Nothing%20less.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20will%20end%20with%20a%20quote%20from%20a%20recent%20article%20by%20our%20cofounder%20Raju%20Rajagopal%20about%20Modi%2C%20Biden%2C%20and%20Human%20Rights%20through%20the%20lens%20of%20the%20Bhagavad%20Gita%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20action%20undertaken%20from%20delusion%2C%3Cbr%3E%20without%20regard%20to%20capacity%20and%20to%20consequences%3Cbr%3E%20%E2%80%93%20loss%20and%20injury%20to%20others%20%E2%80%93%3Cbr%3E%20that%20is%20declared%20to%20be%20dark%20%5Bvikarma%5D.%E2%80%9D%20(XVIII-25)%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECensorship%20alert%3A%20IAMC%20Urgently%20Demands%20Restoration%20of%20X%20Account%20Access%20in%20India%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWashington%2C%20D.C.%20(October%2016%2C%202023)%20%E2%80%94%20The%20Indian%20American%20Muslim%20Council%2C%20the%20U.S.%20oldest%20and%20largest%20advocacy%20organization%20committed%20to%20promoting%20justice%2C%20pluralism%2C%20and%20the%20civil%20rights%20of%20Indian%20Americans%2C%20is%20gravely%20concerned%20by%20the%20censorship%20of%20its%20account%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter%2C%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2014%2C%20IAMC%20and%20its%20close%20ally%20Hindus%20for%20Human%20Rights%20(HFHR)%20learned%20that%20their%20X%20accounts%20were%20withheld%20in%20India%20in%20response%20to%20a%20%E2%80%9Clegal%20demand%E2%80%9D%20from%20the%20Indian%20government.%20Two%20days%20after%20the%20suspension%2C%20X%20wrote%20IAMC%20to%20inform%20that%20the%20account%20has%20been%20withheld%20after%20X%20received%20%E2%80%9Ca%20legal%20removal%20demand%20from%20the%20Government%20of%20India%E2%80%A6%20that%20claims%20the%20following%20content%20violates%20India%E2%80%99s%20Information%20Technology%20Act%2C%202000.%E2%80%9D%20The%20Indian%20government%E2%80%99s%20sweeping%20and%20draconian%20Information%20Technology%20Act%20has%20already%20been%20used%20to%20censor%20many%20online%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIAMC%E2%80%99s%20X%20account%20serves%20as%20an%20important%20medium%20for%20Indian-American%20Muslims%20to%20shine%20light%20on%20Hindu%20nationalism%20and%20worsening%20human%20rights%20conditions%20of%20persecuted%20minority%20groups%20in%20India.%20Silencing%20our%20voice%20on%20social%20media%20is%20an%20affront%20not%20just%20to%20our%20organization%20but%20to%20the%20democracy%20in%20the%20United%20States%20and%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20IAMC%20executive%20director%20Rasheed%20Ahmed.%20%E2%80%9CX%20executive%20Elon%20Musk%20is%20working%20hand%20in%20glove%20with%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20authoritarian%20regime%20to%20block%20a%20U.S.%20based%20organization.%20X%20is%20accelerating%20the%20suppression%20of%20free%20expression%20and%20democracy%20in%20India%20and%20the%20U.S.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20suspension%20of%20IAMC%20and%20HFHR%E2%80%99s%20accounts%20continues%20the%20Indian%20government%E2%80%99s%20broader%20crackdown%20on%20critical%20voices%20in%20media%20and%20politics%2C%20which%20escalated%20in%20recent%20weeks%20with%20the%20Indian%20government%20filing%20criminal%20charges%20against%20prominent%20novelist%20Arundhati%20Roy%20and%20raiding%20the%20offices%20of%20the%20Independent%20news%20organization%20NewsClick%20and%20arresting%20its%20editor-in-chief.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20the%20alleged%20assassination%20of%20Canadian%20resident%20Hardeep%20Singh%20by%20Indian%20foreign%20agents%2C%20the%20censorship%20of%20U.S.%20based%20social%20media%20accounts%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20repressive%20tactics%20now%20clearly%20pose%20an%20international%20threat%20to%20security%20and%20freedom%20of%20expression%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20IAMC%20President%20Mohammad%20Jawad.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIAMC%20calls%20on%20X%20to%20immediately%20restore%20access%20to%20its%20account%20in%20India.%20IAMC%20furthermore%20calls%20on%20the%20aid%20of%20the%20international%20community%20as%20it%20seeks%20to%20counter%20rising%20threats%20to%20its%20freedom%20of%20expression%20in%20India.%20IAMC%20is%20in%20close%20contact%20with%20its%20attorneys%20as%20it%20seeks%20legal%20recourse%20to%20challenge%20the%20withholding%20of%20its%20account.%20It%20joins%20with%20close%20allies%20as%20it%20continues%20to%20fight%20for%20the%20civil%20rights%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20persecuted%20minorities%20and%20on%20behalf%20of%20freedom%20of%20speech%20everywhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697548820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2F23120119%2FWhatsApp-Image-2019-09-23-at-10.07.35.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fwill-not-be-silenced-hindus-for-human-rights-x-account-withheld%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20non-profit%20organisation%20said%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20is%20%26quot%3Bscared%20of%20a%20movement%20of%20progressive%20Hindus%20and%20their%20supporters%20speaking%20up%20to%20save%20Indian%20democracy%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A67%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fwill-not-be-silenced-hindus-for-human-rights-x-account-withheld%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China's%20pitch%20of%20an%20alternative%20world%20will%20guide%20its%20response%20to%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697548620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F1