%3EShe%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CAlso%2C%20one%20must%20take%20a%20two-litre%20bottle%20to%20store%20one%20litre%20of%20mixture%20as%20it%20will%20allow%20some%20space%20for%20fermentation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EKeep%20in%20the%20dark%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EAny%20fertiliser%20must%20be%20stored%20in%20a%20dark%20place%2C%20says%20Nita.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20good%20bacteria%20in%20the%20fertiliser%20will%20die%20if%20the%20containers%20are%20kept%20in%20sunlight.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20spray%20the%20enzymes%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3ENita%20says%20it%20takes%20three%20months%20to%20ready%20the%20enzymes.%20It%20has%20the%20aroma%20of%20a%20vinegar.%20After%20the%20batch%20is%20ready%2C%20gardeners%20can%20mix%201-2%20ml%20of%20enzyme%20in%20a%20litre%20of%20water.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20insect%20attack%20is%20severe%2C%20then%20up%20to%205%20ml%20of%20enzymes%20can%20be%20mixed%20in%20the%20water.%20Spray%20this%20mixture%20onto%20plants%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20make%20the%20second%20batch%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3ENita%20says%20that%20these%20enzymes%20can%20be%20stored%20for%20as%20many%20months%20as%20it%20has%20no%20expiry%20date.%20And%20to%20make%20the%20second%20batch%20process%20faster%2C%20one%20can%20add%20roughly%205%20ml%20of%20enzyme%20to%20the%20new%20batch%2C%20so%20it%20will%20then%20be%20ready%20in%20one%20month!%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697547131000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D332396%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kolkata%20resident%20Nita%20Singh%20started%20gardening%20to%20relive%20childhood%20memories%20of%20her%20grandma%E2%80%99s%20garden.%20Today%2C%20she%20grows%20over%20500%20plants%20of%20diverse%20varieties%20and%20even%20prepares%20her%20own%20bio%20enzymes