0has%20such%20a%20beautiful%20mangrove%20and%20wetland%20habitat%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Vidyasagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVisiting%20the%20numerous%20wetlands%20in%20the%20city%20and%20documenting%20the%20beautiful%20birds%20led%20to%20a%20deeper%20understanding%20about%20the%20issues%20around%20wetlands%20and%20the%20natural%20history%20phenomenon.%20He%20decided%20to%20create%20awareness%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20conserving%20the%20urban%20wetlands%20through%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fflamingosofmumbai%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInstagram%20page.%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHere%20are%2010%20pictures%20that%20show%20how%20important%20it%20is%20to%20preserve%20the%20mangroves%20and%20wetlands%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Col%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20lake%20behind%20the%20NRI%20complex%2C%20Navi%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Fol%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201066px)%20100vw%2C%201066px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPicture-1-1697205202.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221066%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20lake%20behind%20the%20NRI%20complex%2C%20Navi%20Mumbai.%20Image%20credit%3A%20Vidyasagar%20Hariharan%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPicture-1-1697205202.jpeg%201066w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPicture-1-1697205202-200x300.jpeg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPicture-1-1697205202-500x750.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPicture-1-1697205202-768x1153.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPicture-1-1697205202-1023x1536.jpeg%201023w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPicture-1-1697205202-150x225.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332208%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%20Image%20credit%3A%20Vidyasagar%20Hariharan%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20picture%20perfectly%20captures%20how%20humans%20have%20intruded%20into%20animal%20territory.%20Home%20to%20more%20than%2060%20species%20of%20birds%2C%20this%20lake%20is%20under%20threat%2C%20as%20builders%20want%20to%20construct%20a%20golf%20course%20in%20this%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20found%20my%20purpose%20when%20I%20heard%20about%20the%20golf%20course.%20This%20wetland%20lake%20is%20amongst%20the%20three%20in%20Navi%20Mumbai%20that%20are%20crucial%20for%20flamingo%20migration.%20They%20come%20here%20during%20high%20tides%20and%20perform%20their%20mating%20dance%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20photographer.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Col%20start%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20lake%20behind%20the%20NRI%20Complex%2C%20Navi%20Mumbai.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Fol%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPicture-2-min-2-1697205291.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Image%20credit%3A%20Vidyasagar%20Hariharan%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPicture-2-min-2-1697205291.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPicture-2-min-2-1697205291-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPicture-2-min-2-1697205291-500x333.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPicture-2-min-2-1697205291-768x512.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPicture-2-min-2-1697205291-1